<p>Itâ€™s a quick win you can apply to your store before Easter and turn an otherwise regular sale into a virtual event, as Man Crates does.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Suggest Gift Options</strong></h2>



<p>Youâ€™re likely preparingÂ <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-gift-guides&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037738000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2CJKZKJyq_f__hViq7iXZe" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">gift guides</a>Â and recommending different gift options for Christmas andÂ <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/valentines-day-marketing&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037738000&amp;usg=AOvVaw16XTmb79UIDDO9jqzZHT3_" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Valentineâ€™s Day</a>. What you may not be doing is repeating the same for Easter.</p>



