<p>A popup like the above is a must-have especially if you have a dedicated landing page for the sale, or discounting only certain products for Valentineâ€™s Day.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Run a Valentineâ€™s Day Sale</strong></h2>



<p>With millions of consumers gift shopping online, thereâ€™s one way to bring your online store to the forefront of the competition: running a sales campaign.</p>



<p>While offering a compelling <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">discount</a> is key to a successful sales campaign, whatâ€™s more, important is <em>how</em>, <em>when</em>, and <em>where</em> you <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sales-promotion-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">promote</a> your products.</p>



<p>The best way to achieve that is by combining sales popups with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/promotional-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">promotional emails</a>.</p>



<p>Check out this <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">subject line</a> <a href="http://katespade.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Kate Spade</a> uses to announce its Valentineâ€™s Day sale:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="219" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-1024x219.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117106" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-1024x219.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-300x64.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-768x164.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-1536x329.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-380x81.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-600x128.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-760x163.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-1440x308.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-164x35.png 164w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-234x50.png 234w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-740x158.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-220x47.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3-385x82.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-3.png 1594w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>By calling out its subscribers as â€œhey valentine,â€ Kate Spade adds a casual and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-personalization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">personal</a> touch to its email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="636" height="932" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-117107"/></figure></div>



<p>Kate Spade <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-appreciation-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">appreciates its customers</a> by giving them an extra 30 percent off its sale styles. An email like this is a smart way to show some love to your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email list</a> and engage them when theyâ€™re about to shop for gifts.</p>



