<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Offer More Benefits</strong></h2>



<p>While almost every brand offers Valentineâ€™s Day discounts, other incentives, such as free shipping, can differentiate your store from the competition. After all, free shipping is <a href="https://www.walkersands.com/resources/the-future-of-retail-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">one of the top factors</a> that influence online consumersâ€™ buying decisions.</p>



<p>If you canâ€™t afford to offer free shipping all year round, however, consider presenting it as a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">limited-time offer</a> and adding a sense of urgency, like <a href="https://www.madsencycles.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Madsen Cycles</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="597" height="976" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117112" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3.png 597w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-184x300.png 184w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-380x621.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-21x35.png 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-31x50.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-300x490.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-220x360.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-3-385x629.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px" /></figure></div>



<p>While cargo bikes arenâ€™t typical Valentineâ€™s Day gifts, Madsen Cycles finds a point that ties its products to this day. In this email, they offer their subscribers free shipping <em>â€œnow thru Valentineâ€™s Day.â€</em></p>



<p>Itâ€™s a compelling incentive that can work with any holiday, especially for products with higher delivery costs.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.esteelauder.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Estee Lauder</a>, on the other hand, uses free shipping to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/upselling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">upsell</a> during Valentineâ€™s Day:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="868" height="919" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117114" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1.png 868w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-283x300.png 283w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-768x813.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-380x402.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-600x635.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-760x805.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-47x50.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-463x490.png 463w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-220x233.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-1-385x408.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 868px) 100vw, 868px" /></figure>



<p>To claim your free 2-day shipping and to get your perfect gift in time, Estee Lauder asks you to spend over $75. This way, the company smartly takes you to a higher price point and increases conversions by guaranteeing delivery by Valentineâ€™s Day.</p>



<p>If you want to strengthen your hand further, you can offer free gift-wrapping as an extra benefit to save customers from additional trouble.</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Make Your Delivery Dates Visible</strong></h2>



<p>Regardless of the time of the year, delivery is always a soft spot for online shoppers. However, it becomes an even more sensitive concern during the gift shopping season.</p>



<p>When someoneâ€™s about to buy a gift for the special person in their life (to be given at a specific date), the first thing they check is delivery times.</p>



<p>If you want to convert Valentineâ€™s Day shoppers into customers, make your delivery dates clear and visible across your website, as well as in your popups and emails.</p>



<p>Whatâ€™s more, remember to write the last date customers can place orders for Valentineâ€™s Day or when they can expect to get their items delivered.</p>



<p>Take inspiration from <a href="https://www.calvinklein.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Calvin Klein</a>, who does that successfully in its emails:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="808" height="978" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-117115"/></figure></div>



<p>After inviting you to buy a timeless gift for your Valentine and recommending a few products, the company adds a sentence to the bottom of this email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="764" height="989" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117116" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4.png 764w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-232x300.png 232w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-380x492.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-600x777.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-760x984.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-39x50.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-379x490.png 379w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-220x285.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-4-385x498.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 764px) 100vw, 764px" /></figure></div>



<p>Itâ€™s a simple addition that makes a difference for prospects whoâ€™re considering shopping from the company.</p>



<p>If youâ€™re offering multiple shipping options, itâ€™s also important to let your customers know how theyâ€™ll work during this season. Check out this example from <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/meundies-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">MeUndies</a> to see how that might look like:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="972" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-117117"/></figure></div>



<p>The first part of this Valentineâ€™s Day email looks like any other. Yet, when you scroll down the email, you reach this part where MeUndies explains what these different delivery options mean for you:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="678" height="489" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117119" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3.png 678w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-300x216.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-380x274.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-600x433.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-69x50.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-220x159.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-3-385x278.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 678px) 100vw, 678px" /></figure>



<p>This helps the company make it easier to understand your options and clearly communicate when you should expect to receive your items.</p>



<p>Notice how the company goes into detail and even writes down the last hour you should place your order to get your delivery in time.</p>



<p>If you want to inform your website visitors in a similar way, you can create a popup that only shows on your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product pages</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="938" height="917" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117118" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3.png 938w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-300x293.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-768x751.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-380x371.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-600x587.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-760x743.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-36x35.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-51x50.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-501x490.png 501w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-220x215.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-3-385x376.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 938px) 100vw, 938px" /></figure></div>



<p>Using a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/countdown-timer-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">countdown timer</a> in your popup, like the above, can help you create a sense of urgency and increase conversions.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Promote Relevant Products</strong></h2>



<p>Valentineâ€™s Day gifts differ from Christmas or birthday gifts by nature. After all, Valentineâ€™s Day is about love, hearts, and glitterâ€”something you wouldnâ€™t associate with other <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">holidays</a>.</p>



<p>If you sell products around that theme, Valentineâ€™s Day is the perfect time to promote them as ideal gift options. Take a look at this email by <a href="https://cottonbureau.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Cotton Bureau</a> promoting its heart print t-shirts for this day:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="929" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117120" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-226x300.png 226w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-380x504.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-600x796.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-26x35.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-369x490.png 369w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-220x292.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-3-385x511.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



