<p>Although their products arenâ€™t necessarily Valentineâ€™s Day material, Cotton Bureau finds a smart way to link the two.</p>



<p>Even if your products donâ€™t associate with this concept, you can still use Valentineâ€™s Day as an excuse for <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-promotion" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product promotion</a>, just like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sunski-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Sunski</a> does:</p>



