<p>With this email, sent around Valentineâ€™s Day, Sunski simply leverages an association, and promote its rose-colored glasses.</p>



<p>If you want to promote your Valentineâ€™s-themed or discounted products on your site, you can create a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-popups" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product recommendation popup</a>, where you showcase your bestsellers or top picks from the sale:</p>



