<p>Itâ€™s an easy strategy to replicate, whether youâ€™re running a sale or not.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Offer Gift Guides</strong></h2>



<p>If there were ever a perfect time to guide prospects with relevant and helpful gift guides, itâ€™s in the days leading up to Valentineâ€™s Day.</p>



<p>By offering gift guides in the form of emails, popups, or <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-landing-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">landing pages</a>, you can help your prospects make a better buying decision and position your products as great gift ideas.</p>



<p>You can take the easy road with gender-based categories or go deeper into personality and interests. In this email, <a href="https://huckberry.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Huckberry</a> does both:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="676" height="916" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117124" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1.png 676w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-221x300.png 221w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-380x515.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-600x813.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-26x35.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-37x50.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-362x490.png 362w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-220x298.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image36-1-385x522.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 676px) 100vw, 676px" /></figure></div>



<p>The company sends its gift guides in a long newsletter format, where they organize gifts, first, by category and then, by gender:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="588" height="1014" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117125" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3.png 588w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-174x300.png 174w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-380x655.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-20x35.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-29x50.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-284x490.png 284w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-220x379.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-3-385x664.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 588px) 100vw, 588px" /></figure></div>



<p>With this approach, the company makes its content easy to skim through. If your Valentine is, say, an adventurer, you can quickly start browsing from this category.</p>



<p>If your products are already targeting a specific hobby or gender, you can expand your gift guides even further, as <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/man-crates-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Man Crates</a> does:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="607" height="977" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117126" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3.png 607w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-186x300.png 186w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-380x612.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-600x966.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-22x35.png 22w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-31x50.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-304x490.png 304w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-220x354.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-3-385x620.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 607px) 100vw, 607px" /></figure></div>



<p>With a benefit-driven headline that reads â€œGet him a gift that gets him,â€ Man Crates highlights that people are different, and so are their tastes in gifts.</p>



<p>In this gift guide email, Man Crates curates different gift options based on personality types in their signature <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/funny-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">humorous tone</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="819" height="1016" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117127" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3.png 819w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-242x300.png 242w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-768x953.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-380x471.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-600x744.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-760x943.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-395x490.png 395w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-220x273.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-3-385x478.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px" /></figure></div>



<p>If youâ€™re interested in any of these categories, you can click through and learn more about each product type or visit a landing page where you can filter and sort different gift options.</p>



