<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Drive Urgency</strong></h2>



<p>Combining <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">scarcity-driven</a> copy with a countdown timer is a great way of driving urgency in last-minute buyers.</p>



<p>The key is to do this without making people feel guilty. Check out how <a href="https://www.mancrates.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Man Crates</a> does that in a fun way:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="1013" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117129" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-207x300.png 207w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-380x550.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-600x868.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-24x35.png 24w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-339x490.png 339w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-220x318.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image39-385x557.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>In this email, the brand simply informs you that today is the last day to guarantee your Valentineâ€™s Day delivery.</p>



<p>Man Crates cleverly communicates urgency with humor by saying â€œTrue love might wait, but our delivery team canâ€™t.â€</p>



<p><a href="https://www.marcjacobs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Marc Jacobs</a>, on the other hand, chooses another way to imply urgency without stressing prospects out:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="215" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-1024x215.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117130" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-1024x215.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-300x63.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-768x161.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-380x80.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-600x126.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-760x160.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-1440x303.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-166x35.png 166w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-238x50.png 238w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-740x156.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-220x46.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3-385x81.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-3.png 1484w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>In this subject line, the company simply suggests placing your order in good time so that you can get <em>their </em>gifts by Valentineâ€™s Day.</p>



<p>When you open the email, this is what you see:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="620" height="934" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image37.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-117131"/></figure></div>



<p>An ordinary promotional email with delivery information. But when you scroll down to the remainder of the email, you see this:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117132" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-768x371.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-760x367.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-3.png 1119w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Marc Jacobs repeats their CTA with subtle urgency and supports it by showing different delivery options, following Strategy #4.</p>



<p>Rather than vaguely saying â€œGet it before Valentineâ€™s Day,â€ the company backs up its claims for urgency and scarcity with actual delivery dates.</p>



<p>If you want to create the same feeling among your website visitors, remember to add a similar popup to your product pages with a countdown timer, visible delivery dates, and an urgency-driven CTA.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="893" height="847" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117133" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2.png 893w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-300x285.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-768x728.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-380x360.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-600x569.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-760x721.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-517x490.png 517w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-220x209.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-2-385x365.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 893px) 100vw, 893px" /></figure>



<h2 id="8"><strong>8. Target Last-Minute Shoppers</strong></h2>



<p>Some of us are chronic procrastinators, and shopping for last-minute gifts, for many, is no exception.</p>



<p>While many e-tailers chase after last-minute shoppers by triggering a sense of guilt, thereâ€™s a more effective way to convert procrastinators into customers.</p>



<p>If you can offer fast delivery to last-minute customers, youâ€™re ten steps ahead of the competition. <a href="https://www.violetgrey.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Violet Grey</a> is one such brand and uses fast delivery to sell more on Valentineâ€™s Day:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="607" height="978" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117134" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3.png 607w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-186x300.png 186w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-380x612.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-600x967.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-22x35.png 22w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-31x50.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-304x490.png 304w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-220x354.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-3-385x620.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 607px) 100vw, 607px" /></figure></div>



<p>First, the company targets procrastinators with a curated list of â€œlast-minute beauty gifts.â€ Whatâ€™s more, they offer overnight and same-day shippingâ€”but only when you spend over $150.</p>



<p>If you want to get your gifts in time, you end up buying more expensive items. This way, Violet Grey not only captures last-minute shoppers but also upsells them.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.curioos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Curioos</a> chooses a different way to engage last-minute shoppers without breaking the bank:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="821" height="971" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117135" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1.png 821w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-254x300.png 254w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-768x908.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-380x449.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-600x710.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-760x899.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-42x50.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-414x490.png 414w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-220x260.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image35-1-385x455.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 821px) 100vw, 821px" /></figure></div>



<p>The company recommends its electronic gift cards as a Valentineâ€™s Day gift option and makes them more attractive with a discount. Whatâ€™s more, Curioos handles any possible objections by saying â€œno fees or expiration dates.â€</p>



<p>If youâ€™re offering gift cards on your site, holidays are perfect for targeting late gift shoppers without hurting your profits.</p>



<h2 id="9"><strong>9. Redefine Valentineâ€™s Day</strong></h2>



<p>Valentineâ€™s Day isnâ€™t for every brand (or person for that matter). Yet, you can still take advantage of this special day by redefining it for your brand.</p>



<p>Depending on the nature of your products and your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">value proposition</a>, you can take an anti-Valentineâ€™s Day position or support singles on this day with your products. Alternatively, you can celebrate a made-up holiday that fits your brand.</p>



<p>Thatâ€™s what <a href="https://www.woolandthegang.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Wool and the Gang</a> does:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="648" height="936" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-117136"/></figure>



<p>Instead of focusing on Valentineâ€™s Day, the company celebrates <em>Galentineâ€™s Day </em>on February 13th. In case youâ€™re unfamiliar with the concept, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Galentine%27s_Day" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Galentineâ€™s Day</a> is simply a day where â€œladies celebrate ladiesâ€ (created by <em>Parks and Recreation&#8217;s</em> Leslie Knope.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="357" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Leslie-Knope-Galentines-Day.gif" alt="Leslie Knope Galentines Day" class="wp-image-89368"/></figure></div>



<p>In this email, Wool and the Gang humanize their brand by inviting you to their Instagram page to learn about the teamâ€™s girl crushes. Next, they recommend products as part of their Galentineâ€™s gift guide and take you to a dedicated landing page:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="527" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-1024x527.png" alt="Wool and the Gang Galentines Day Landing Page" class="wp-image-89456" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-1024x527.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-300x154.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-768x395.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-1536x790.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-380x195.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-600x309.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-760x391.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-1440x741.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Galentines-Day-Landing-Page-740x381.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2