<p>Itâ€™s a simple tactic that helps Wool and the Gang stand out among thousands of online stores celebrating Valentineâ€™s Day, and subtly promote their products.</p>



<h2 id="10"><strong>10. Appreciate Your Subscribers</strong></h2>



<p>Regardless of its origins, Valentineâ€™s Day is associated with love and romance.</p>



<p>That being the case, Valentineâ€™s Day is an excellent opportunity to show some love to your email list. Many online stores already use this day to appreciate their subscribers and subtly promote their products. <a href="https://www.kikki-k.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">kikki.K</a> is one of those brands:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="311" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line.png" alt="kikki.K Subject Line" class="wp-image-89356" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-113x50.png 113w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Subject-Line-385x171.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>This personal-sounding subject line easily stands out in your inbox full of promotional Valentineâ€™s Day emails. Similarly, the email itself resembles a personal Valentineâ€™s card (or rather, a collection of Valentineâ€™s Day cards):</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="648" height="890" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email.gif" alt="kikki.K Valentines Day Email" class="wp-image-89360"/></figure></div>



<p>Although kikki.K genuinely celebrates its subscribers, the company actually promotes its new arrivals in this email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="957" height="962" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email.png" alt="kikki.K Valentines Day Email" class="wp-image-89364" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email.png 957w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-298x300.png 298w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-150x150.png 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-768x772.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-380x382.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-600x603.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-760x764.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-50x50.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-487x490.png 487w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-220x221.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-385x387.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Valentines-Day-Email-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 957px) 100vw, 957px" /></figure></div>



<p>Yet, they cleverly frame it around the love theme.</p>



<p>Valentineâ€™s theme isnâ€™t only great for promoting your products in disguise. It can also help you keep your subscribers engaged, collect <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-feedback" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">customer feedback</a>, or promote your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">customer loyalty program</a>.</p>



<p><a href="https://tartecosmetics.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Tarte</a> chooses the last objective and sends this email with the subject line <em>â€œAn Early Valentine For You <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f48c.png" alt="ğŸ’Œ" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />â€:</em></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="744" height="860" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Valentines-Day-Email.gif" alt="Tarte Valentines Day Email" class="wp-image-89428"/></figure></div>



<p>The email successfully evokes curiosity by imitating a mysterious love letter. When you click the CTA button, you find out more about the surprise of your secret admirer:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="750" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-1024x750.png" alt="Tarte Rewards Landing Page" class="wp-image-89424" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-1024x750.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-768x562.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-380x278.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-600x439.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-760x557.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-669x490.png 669w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Rewards-Landing-Page.png 1259w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>You get to learn that Tarte is, somewhat frustratingly, promoting its rewards program with this mysterious email.</p>



<p>Itâ€™s hard to draw a line, but be mindful of the expectations you set in these types of emails and try to deliver on your word.</p>



