<p>This strategy isnâ€™t for everybody (and it certainly isnâ€™t a last-minute project) but if you have the resources to go the extra mile, itâ€™s perfect for creating exclusivity and driving <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">scarcity</a>.</p>



