<p>Imagine, then, that you see a unique popup like this, instead:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="921" height="510" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example.png" alt="SiteData Popup Example" class="wp-image-115842" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example.png 921w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-760x421.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-740x410.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-385x213.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 921px) 100vw, 921px" /></figure>



<p>This one aligns with your interests, feels personal, and meets your needs at the right stage of the buying process. Thatâ€™s exactly what you can achieve with SiteData: show a personalized popup to each visitor, based on the information <em>that matters to them.</em></p>



<p>With SiteData, you can use any visitor data youâ€™re collecting as merge tags in your popups and customize your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-copywriting">popup copy</a> dynamically for each visitor.</p>



<p>For example, you can greet a returning visitor by their first name when they log in to your site, and only use the information thatâ€™s relevant to them, such as location:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="712" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name.png" alt="SiteData Popup Example First Name" class="wp-image-115839" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-300x215.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-768x551.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-380x273.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-600x431.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-760x545.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-683x490.png 683w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-220x158.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-First-Name-385x276.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>If youâ€™re a SaaS marketer, youâ€™re likely trying to turn free trials into paying customers and small plans into long-term subscriptions. With SiteData, you can invite users to upgrade to a higher planâ€”but only after they log in to your website, and by referring to their company name and the plan theyâ€™re on.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="673" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-1024x673.png" alt="SiteData Popup Example 2" class="wp-image-115840" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-1024x673.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-300x197.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-768x505.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-380x250.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-600x394.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-760x499.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-53x35.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-76x50.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-740x486.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-220x145.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2-385x253.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Popup-Example-2.png 1251w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>In both cases, your popups become more relevant to the visitor, making it easier for them to take action.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Build a Popup Sequence</strong></h2>



<p>It often takes more than one touchpoint to turn a visitor into a customer.</p>



<p>In a typical <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey">buyer&#8217;s journey</a>, you first capture a visitorâ€™s email address with a popup to convince them to continue shopping. A better way to do this is to build a popup sequence, so you can engage your new subscribers without waiting.</p>



<p>You can send the information your visitors submit in one popup to SiteData, and use it to show, hide, or personalize another popup.</p>



<p>Once you get the data about your new signups, such as name or gender, you can use them to show targeted popups that grab their attention.</p>



<p>In your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-popup-examples">email popup</a>, you can ask for the visitorâ€™s name and email address:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="705" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-1024x705.png" alt="Multistep Popup" class="wp-image-115838" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-1024x705.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-300x206.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-768x529.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-380x262.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-600x413.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-760x523.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-712x490.png 712w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-220x151.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-385x265.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup.png 1248w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Then, in the second step, you can learn more about your new subscriberâ€™s gender, country, interests, and so on:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="507" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-1024x507.png" alt="Multistep Popup 2" class="wp-image-115837" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-1024x507.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-768x381.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-600x297.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-760x377.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-740x367.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2-385x191.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Multistep-Popup-2.png 1322w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>After visitors submit their information, they will see a second popup on the next page, which builds upon the first message and matches their interests:</p>



