<p>You can add a third or fourth popup based on your goals and take full control of the buyerâ€™s journey with your popups that show to the right people at the ideal time.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Pro Tip: </strong>If you promise a discount code upon signup in your first popup, this <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-popups">product recommendation popup</a> makes a brilliant followup to use their code right away.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Collect Emails Based on Interests</strong></h2>



<p>Itâ€™s one thing to ask visitors to sign up for your newsletter, and another to give them a valid reason to do so.</p>



<p>By determining your visitorsâ€™ interests and personalizing your popups for each, you can <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies">grow your email list</a> with highly segmented leads.</p>



<p>One way of doing this is to base your popups on the visitorâ€™s page views. If youâ€™re in e-commerce, this could be the products, categories, or brands a visitor is viewing in that session.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="609" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-1024x609.png" alt="SiteData Use Case" class="wp-image-115835" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-1024x609.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-300x178.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-768x457.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-380x226.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-600x357.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-760x452.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-740x440.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-220x131.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-385x229.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case.png 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Itâ€™s a smart way to collect targeted leads whoâ€™ll likely be interested in your offers the next time your products go on sale. Whatâ€™s more, you can now show popups about Bialetti products to the visitors who signed up through this popup. (Remember Use Case #2.)</p>



<p>If you have multiple categories on your site, such as different types of insurance or travel packages, articles, or videos, you can use a similar approach to attract targeted newsletter subscribers.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="941" height="783" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags.png" alt="SiteData Merge Tags" class="wp-image-115834" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags.png 941w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-300x250.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-768x639.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-380x316.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-600x499.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-760x632.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-589x490.png 589w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-220x183.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Merge-Tags-385x320.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 941px) 100vw, 941px" /></figure>



<p>Use SiteData to replace the interested category with dynamic content and youâ€™ll see the difference in your conversions.</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Reduce Cart Abandonment (the Right Way)</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-strategy">Cart abandonment</a> is an everyday struggle for e-commerce marketers.</p>



<p>You know that you need to send the right emails and leverage <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent-popup-examples">exit-intent popups</a> to prevent cart abandonment. You also know that offering discounts can stop visitors from leaving your site.</p>



<p>Although incentives like discounts, free shipping, or gifts work like a charm, they also hurt your profit margins.</p>



<p>A smarter way to incentivize abandoning visitors is to change your reward based on how much theyâ€™re about to spend. In other words, use big incentives as carrots, but only when deserved.</p>



<p>If you offer free shipping for orders over $100 and the visitor only has $10 in their cart, your popup will likely have little influence on convincing them to stay.</p>



<p>My suggestion is to show two different popups based on the visitorâ€™s basket value.&nbsp;</p>



<p>If they have more than $100 in their cart, you can show a popup promising a free gift:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="589" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-1024x589.png" alt="Cart Abandonment Popup" class="wp-image-115832" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-1024x589.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-300x173.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-768x442.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-380x219.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-600x345.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-760x437.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-87x50.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-740x426.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-385x222.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup.png 1359w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>If their cart value is below $100, you can offer a chance to win that product if they complete their purchase:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="564" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-1024x564.png" alt="Cart Abandonment Popup 2" class="wp-image-115833" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-1024x564.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-300x165.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-768x423.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-1536x847.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-380x209.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-600x331.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-760x419.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-1440x794.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-91x50.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-740x408.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-220x121.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2-385x212.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-2.png 1593w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>This way, you always show the right kind of incentive to the right people and prevent cart abandonment without breaking the bank.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Upsell With an Incentive</strong></h2>



<p>Although <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-popup-examples">cart abandonment popups</a> help you reclaim otherwise lost sales, you donâ€™t need to wait until visitors decide to leave, to increase your revenue.</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/upselling">Upselling</a>, the strategy of inviting customers to spend more, can be highly effective when coupled with a compelling incentiveâ€”and used at the right time and place.</p>



<p>When a visitor has an empty cart, your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action">call to action</a> to â€œspend $100 moreâ€ to qualify for an incentive will likely have little success. Or worse, you may come off as too salesy and risk the visitor leaving your store.</p>



<p>Try asking the same question, only after the visitor adds a product to their cart instead, and your request will be more relevant. Whatâ€™s better, you can send visitorsâ€™ basket value to SiteData and show how much more they need to spend to qualify for free shipping in your popups:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="994" height="744" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData.png" alt="Upsell Popup SiteData" class="wp-image-115831" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData.png 994w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-300x225.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-768x575.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-380x284.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-600x449.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-760x569.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-655x490.png 655w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-220x165.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Upsell-Popup-SiteData-385x288.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px" /></figure>



<p>If you want to make the decision easier for your customers, you can add personalized recommendations to your upsell popup, based on the products in their cart:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="755" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-1024x755.png" alt="SiteData Recommendation Popup" class="wp-image-115843" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-1024x755.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-300x221.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-768x566.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-380x280.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-600x443.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-760x561.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-664x490.png 664w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-220x162.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup-385x284.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Recommendation-Popup.png 1246w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Upselling with an incentive is a clever way of taking customers to a higher price point and itâ€™s even more effective with SiteData.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Cross-Sell With Relevant Recommendations</strong></h2>



<p>Using incentives like the above is only one way to increase customersâ€™ <a href="https://sleeknote.com/recipes/how-to-increase-your-customers-average-order-value">average order value</a>.</p>



<p>Another, completely free and useful, method to do so is to recommend relevant products based on the items that are already in the visitorâ€™s basket.</p>



<p>If youâ€™re tracking the brands or product categories in a visitorâ€™s cart, you can send this information to SiteData and use it to show the right popup. In it, you can make recommendations that complement their soon-to-be-placed order.</p>



<p>For example, if a visitor is about to buy a bed, you can recommend bedding:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-1024x495.png" alt="SiteData Cross-Sell Popup" class="wp-image-115830" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-768x371.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-1536x742.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-760x367.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-1440x696.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Cross-Sell-Popup.png 1771w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Since pillows are much cheaper than a bed, itâ€™s an easier commitment for customers to make. Plus, itâ€™s highly relevant.</p>



<p>If you want to go one step further, you could, for example, recommend products that go well with the items that are in a visitorâ€™s basket. Depending on the tags youâ€™re using on your store, you can base your recommendations on color, size, quantity, price, and so on.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="765" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell.png" alt="SiteData Use Case Cross-Sell" class="wp-image-115829" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-300x224.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-768x574.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-380x284.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-600x448.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-760x568.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-656x490.png 656w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-220x164.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Cross-Sell-385x288.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>With a cross-sell popup that works with SiteData, you can increase average value and guide visitors to better buying decisions at the same time.</p>



<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Drive More App Installs</strong></h2>



<p>As mobile e-commerce keeps growing, many e-tailers now offer mobile apps for a smooth shopping experience. And itâ€™s for a good reason: On average, apps have a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/mobile-commerce-statistics">14 percent higher conversion rate</a> than mobile browsers.</p>



<p>Popups are the most effective way to channel your mobile visitors into your apps and leverage your mobile traffic the best way possible.</p>



<p>However, you need to make sure that youâ€™re guiding the right people to the right app store to avoid interrupting mobile visitors with irrelevant information.</p>



<p>With SiteData, you can easily detect the visitorâ€™s operating system and send them to the right app store to drive installs.</p>



<p>If the visitor is using an Apple device, they can see this popup:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="503" height="876" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App.png" alt="SiteData Use Case Mobile App" class="wp-image-115828" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App.png 503w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-172x300.png 172w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-380x662.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-20x35.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-29x50.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-281x490.png 281w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-220x383.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-385x670.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px" /></figure></div>



<p>And if theyâ€™re an Android user, a second popup shows to them:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="518" height="911" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2.png" alt="SiteData Use Case Mobile App 2" class="wp-image-115827" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2.png 518w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-171x300.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-380x668.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-20x35.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-28x50.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-279x490.png 279w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-220x387.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SiteData-Use-Case-Mobile-App-2-385x677.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px" /></figure></div>



<p>It only takes two popups (and no developers. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f913.png" alt="ğŸ¤“" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />)</p>



<p>If you only want to reach your existing customers, you can show your popup when they log in to your customer area and hide it from other visitors. This way, you can focus your efforts on turning prospects into customers, with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sales-promotion-popup-examples">promotional popups</a>.</p>


