<p>In this cleverly designed email campaign, you promise to take care of your hair, and the way to do this is, unsurprisingly, using Function of Beautyâ€™s products.<br></p>



<p>In the rest of the email, you see a headline that reads â€œMeet Custom Hair Mask,â€ after which the company asserts your <em>wants </em>and <em>needs:</em><br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="931" height="635" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2.png" alt="Function of Beauty Email 2" class="wp-image-82151" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2.png 931w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-300x205.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-768x524.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-380x259.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-600x409.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-760x518.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-718x490.png 718w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-220x150.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Function-of-Beauty-Email-2-385x263.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 931px) 100vw, 931px" /></figure></div>



<p>The <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> (CTA) button â€œOrder Nowâ€ sends you to a hair quiz you can take to create and purchase your custom hair mask.<br></p>



<p>Thanks to this fun promotional email, Function of Beauty explains the problem theyâ€™re solving (read: their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">value proposition</a>) in a creative and memorable way.<br></p>



