<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Keep Your Readers Engaged (Boxycharm)</strong></h2>



<p>Itâ€™s no secret that eye-catching subject lines get your emails opened. But what makes people read your emails all the way to the end?<br></p>



<p>With more than <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/456500/daily-number-of-e-mails-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">250 billion</a> emails sent and received every day, users canâ€™t help but skim through their busy inboxes.<br></p>



<p>In other words, the emails you spent hours writing can go unnoticed (even with an outstanding subject line.)<br></p>



<p>This is especially true if youâ€™re writing long emails containing several products.<br></p>



<p>By using <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/visual-cues" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">visual cues</a>, you can guide subscribers to the most critical part of your emails, and nudge people to read through your emails.<br></p>



<p>Evoking curiosity is the best way to achieve that, and <a href="http://boxycharm.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Boxycharm</a> has a great example of that.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="189" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-1024x189.png" alt="Boxycharm Subject Line" class="wp-image-82115" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-1024x189.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-300x55.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-768x142.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-1536x283.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-380x70.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-600x111.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-760x140.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-1440x266.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-180x33.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-250x46.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-740x137.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-220x41.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line-385x71.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Subject-Line.png 1610w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Coupled with a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity-infused</a> subject line, the company promotes its products with the following email:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="948" height="948" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email.gif" alt="Boxycharm Email" class="wp-image-82111"/></figure></div>



<p>Whatâ€™s interesting is Boxycharm uses an animated arrow to direct your attention several times throughout the email.</p>







<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="582" height="802" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-2.gif" alt="Boxycharm Email 2" class="wp-image-82103"/></figure></div>



<p>Knowing that we all love surprises, Boxycharm holds your attention with the promise of a surprise.<br></p>



<p>And when you scroll down, Boxycharm delivers on its word:<br><br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="982" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3.png" alt="Boxycharm Email 3" class="wp-image-82107" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-183x300.png 183w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-380x622.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-21x35.png 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-31x50.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-299x490.png 299w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-220x360.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boxycharm-Email-3-385x630.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>Itâ€™s a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">limited-time</a> freebie you can claim when you buy the companyâ€™s products.<br></p>



<p>In this email, Boxycharm, first, highlights the scarcity of their products. Then, they focus on the value youâ€™ll get upon purchasing them. Finally, they try to convert you with a time-bound, free gift.<br></p>



<p>The best part is, they help you read through all of these messages, using visual cues.<br></p>



<p>You donâ€™t necessarily need to draw down arrows to get your emails read until the end. Tease your surprise offer or set expectations about the content of your emails in the introduction copy, and youâ€™ll evoke subscribersâ€™ curiosity.<br></p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Make Your Sales Memorable (Brooklinen)</strong></h2>



<p>Itâ€™s a question all marketers consider:<br></p>



<p>How can you sell with email when most customer inboxes are full of promotional emails?<br></p>



