<p>Itâ€™s almost impossible to resist such a curiosity-triggering subject line. As a result, you open the email immediately to see this:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="568" height="920" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Email.gif" alt="Brooklinen Email" class="wp-image-82127"/></figure></div>



