<p>With copy like â€œSomething big is comingâ€ and a GIF unwrapping itself before you, Brooklinen further evokes your curiosity by teasing their upcoming sale.<br></p>



<p>They donâ€™t let you see the discount amount, but they make sure youâ€™re hooked enough to check back again.<br></p>



