<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Tease Your Black Friday Campaign (Chubbies)</strong></h2>



<p>Itâ€™s impossible to ignore <a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Chubbies</a> when discussing Black Friday and good email examples.<br></p>



<p>Known for their exceptional email marketing and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/humor-in-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">humorous</a> tone, Chubbies takes Black Friday campaigns to the next level.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at this subject line and sender name Chubbies uses a week before Black Friday:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="410" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-1024x410.png" alt="Chubbies Black Friday Subject Line" class="wp-image-82147" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-1024x410.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-300x120.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-768x307.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-380x152.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-600x240.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-760x304.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-88x35.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-125x50.png 125w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-740x296.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-220x88.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1-385x154.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Subject-Line-1.png 1225w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>I donâ€™t want to be the type that explains a joke, but with this absurd subject line and matching sender name, Chubbies easily grabs your attention and makes you open the email right away.<br></p>



<p>In the body of the email, Chubbies promotes its upcoming Black Friday offersâ€¦<br></p>



