<p>Thanks to this email, Chubbies gets you excited about both Black Friday, Thighber Monday, and their new product line in one fell swoop.<br></p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Follow Up on Sale Campaigns (Rifle Paper Co.)</strong></h2>



<p>Not all subscribers are ready to buy from you. Thatâ€™s a given.<br></p>



<p>Some will take more persuasion, which means more follow-up emails. One challenge facing many marketers, however, is to follow up on a sale campaign without being pushy.<br></p>



<p>Luckily, <a href="https://riflepaperco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Rifle Paper Co.</a> found a solution to that problem:<br></p>



