<p>On it, Care/of explains which supplements you should take, along with reasons, rather than hard-selling you if youâ€™re not ready to buy.<br></p>



<p>Now that the company knows a lot about you, they can remarket to you with paid ads and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email marketing</a>, using highly personalized recommendations and incentives.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Use a third-party service, such as <a href="https://www.typeform.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Typeform</a>, to create quizzes that are relevant and interesting for ToFu prospects.</li><li>Give users a valid reason to submit their email address.</li><li>Follow up on your new, segmented leads with highly targeted email campaigns.</li></ul>




</div></div>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Offer Gift Guides (Year Round)</strong></h2>



<p>The <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">holiday shopping season</a> is the perfect opportunity to boost e-commerce sales and promote giftable products. With <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Black Friday</a>, Cyber Monday, and Christmas, the holiday season is a highly profitable period for e-commerce marketers.<br></p>



<p>Many online stores create <a href="http://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-gift-guides" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">holiday gift guides</a> for Christmas, New Yearâ€™s, or Valentineâ€™s Day to suggest relevant gift ideas to their visitors. But why stop there while every day is a good day to give gifts?<br></p>



<p>Instead of waiting for highly competitive shopping days, you can suggest gift ideas all year round and guide your visitors into making meaningful purchases.<br></p>



<p>Check out this on-site gift guide example by <a href="https://www.bando.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Ban.do</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="900" height="786" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide.png" alt="Bando Gift Guide" class="wp-image-88064" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide.png 900w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-300x262.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-768x671.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-380x332.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-600x524.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-760x664.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-40x35.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-57x50.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-561x490.png 561w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-220x192.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bando-Gift-Guide-385x336.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></figure></div>



<p>Notice how the company categorizes different gift options by â€œour faves, gifts under $25, gifts under $50.â€ Ban.do also lets you refine your choices using the filters on the left and find the perfect gift youâ€™ve been looking for.<br></p>



<p>This is a great gift guide example because itâ€™s easy-to-navigate, and it helps visitors with their gift search.<br></p>



<p>Email marketing is another channel you can use to distribute your gift guides all year round.<br></p>



<p>Take inspiration from <a href="https://tattly.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Tattly</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="702" height="678" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-1.gif" alt="Tattly Gift Guide Email" class="wp-image-88184"/></figure></div>



<p>The company sends out their holiday gift guide via an email that leads you to their website.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="987" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1.png" alt="Tattly Gift Guide Email 2" class="wp-image-88180" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-213x300.png 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-380x536.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-600x846.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-348x490.png 348w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-220x310.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tattly-Gift-Guide-Email-2-1-385x543.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you scroll further down in the email, you can see how they categorize their gift guides and know what to expect.<br></p>



<p>If you want to take it one step further, you can make excuses to celebrate the little things in life and create your own holidays. Itâ€™s a good way to bond with your future (and existing) customers and promote your products throughout the year.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Create specific, relevant, and easy-to-sort gift guides on your website.</li><li>Add filters and categories for easier navigation.</li><li>Support your gift guides with emails to create excitement.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Convert Empty Shopping Carts</strong></h2>



<p>In an ideal scenario, prospects would likely land on your homepage, click a category, and from there, go to a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product page</a> before moving onto <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">checkout</a>.<br></p>



<p>But in the real world, the buyerâ€™s journey isnâ€™t linear.<br></p>



<p>When a ToFu stage prospect ends up on an under-optimized page, such as <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-404-pages" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">404 pages</a> a sold-out product page, it often becomes the endpoint of their journey.<br></p>



<p>Few e-commerce brands consider this, but <a href="https://www.vinomofo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Vinomofo</a> is an exception.<br></p>



<p>When you click the shopping cart icon and go to your basket page without adding any items, this is what you see:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="740" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-1024x740.png" alt="Vinomofo Empty Cart Page" class="wp-image-88208" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-1024x740.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-300x217.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-768x555.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-380x275.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-600x434.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-760x549.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-69x50.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-678x490.png 678w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-220x159.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page-385x278.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Empty-Cart-Page.png 1266w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The company greets you with an assertive message that reads, â€œWe can only assume thatâ€™s because you havenâ€™t seen our awesome deals yetâ€ and recommends products that are currently on sale.<br></p>



<p>Also, notice how they create <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">social proof</a> by highlighting the number of customers they have and the number of bottles they sold.<br></p>



<p>Following the recommendations comes a CTA button that takes you back to their homepage, in case youâ€™re looking for something other than these deals.<br></p>



<p>Itâ€™s a brilliant strategy for guiding visitors in the right direction and bringing otherwise-lost ToFu leads back on track.<br></p>



<p>If you want to convert empty carts without completely overdoing your checkout process, you can create a <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-popups" target="_blank">product recommendation popup</a> that shows on your cart URL:</p>


