<p>When youâ€™re about to buy one of its products, MeUndies offers you a membership upgrade and a better price. While doing that, they highlight the obvious benefit of membership (save 22%) and contrast it with a one-time purchase ($14/month).<br></p>



<p>If youâ€™re not a MeUndies subscriber, you pass on an exclusive member price, and that sounds too good to overlook.<br></p>



<p>Another brilliant example comes from <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/beardbrand-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Beardbrand</a>:<br></p>



