<p>Upgrading to a Beardbrand subscription not only means saving money but also includes free shipping. Tempting, isnâ€™t it?<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Display the benefits of membership on product pages clearly.</li><li>Show price comparisons to members and non-members.</li><li>Make the subscription option stand out in your design.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2><strong>Part 2: MoFu Strategies</strong></h2>



<p>Middle-of-the-funnel (MoFu) prospects are users that engage with your emails or products but havenâ€™t made a purchase yet.<br></p>



<p>In other words, MoFu leads took a step towards you, and now itâ€™s your turn to make a move.<br></p>



<p>At this stage of the funnel, you need to stay top-of-mind of your prospects and remove any obstacles that are stopping them from making a purchase. A special offer on an abandoned cart or a wishlist item can help nudge MoFu leads further.<br></p>



<p>Here are four outstanding Mo-Fu strategies.<br></p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Stay Top-of-Mind</strong></h2>



<p>If youâ€™re running sales campaigns, youâ€™re likely sending out <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/promotional-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">promotional emails</a> to inform as many subscribers as possible.<br></p>



<p>In addition to their communicative purpose, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sales-promotion-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">sales promotion</a> emails also help you activate mid-funnel prospects that have purchase intent, by providing them with compelling incentives. Plus, they help you stay top-of-mind of your subscribers.<br></p>



<p>One foolproof way to make your sales campaigns memorable, especially during busy times like Black Friday or Christmas, is to send out calendar invite emails.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://www.glossier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Glossier</a> does that successfully:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="692" height="946" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Reminder-Email.gif" alt="Glossier Black Friday Reminder Email" class="wp-image-88156"/></figure></div>



<p>A few hours before Black Friday, Glossier sends this email to its subscribers, asking them to be prepared for the big sale. Rather than only write â€œbe prepared,â€ the company also gives you the option to download its event invite and save the date to your calendar.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="747" height="449" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite.png" alt="Glossier Black Friday Invite" class="wp-image-88152" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite.png 747w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-380x228.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-600x361.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-740x445.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Glossier-Black-Friday-Invite-385x231.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 747px) 100vw, 747px" /></figure></div>



<p>This way, Glossier finds a way to sneak into its MoFu leadsâ€™ minds, calendars, and wallets during a hectic shopping season.<br></p>



<p>The best part? Itâ€™s super easy to replicate for your business and works all year round.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>A few days before your next sales campaign, write a simple <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/announcement-email-examples" target="_blank">announcement email</a> and attach a .ics file.</li><li>Frame your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email copy</a> around exclusivity and thank subscribers for being on your email list.</li><li>Remember to include a description and a website link in your calendar event.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Convert Wishlists with Discounts</strong></h2>



<p>How many times did you add something to your wishlist and never look at it again?<br></p>



<p>Iâ€™ve done it several times.<em> </em>Unless I miraculously get a random urge to buy my wishlist items,<em> I simply forget about their existence.</em><br></p>



<p>As an e-commerce marketer, you canâ€™t ignore your prospectsâ€™ wishlists because they have a high potential to convert. The name itself suggests that your visitors <em>wish </em>to buy those items. And if they abandon their lists without completing the purchase, they must be missing somethingâ€”like a gentle nudge or an incentive.<br></p>



<p>One way to reactivate forgotten list items is to send wishlist reminder emails. You need to display wishlist items with a clear and simple design and add a powerful CTA to help your visitors re-consider the purchase.<br></p>



<p>But how do you encourage visitors to create wishlists in the first place?<br></p>



<p>Look at how <a href="https://www.chairish.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Chairish</a> does it:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="674" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email.gif" alt="Chairish Wishlist Email" class="wp-image-88136"/></figure></div>



<p>Shortly after creating an account on the Chairish website, I received this <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/welcome-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">welcome email</a> asking me to find my favorites. My motivation? Getting notified of when my favorite items go on sale.<br></p>



<p>Like this:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="556" height="562" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email.png" alt="Chairish Wishlist Email" class="wp-image-88140" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email.png 556w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-297x300.png 297w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-380x384.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-485x490.png 485w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-220x222.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-385x389.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chairish-Wishlist-Email-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px" /></figure></div>



<p>I now have a good reason to start a wishlist and am more likely to buy my favorites when they are on sale.<br></p>



<p>If youâ€™re willing to discount your products, you can create a special code that applies to your subscribersâ€™ wishlist items. This way, youâ€™ll create a feeling of <em>exclusivity</em> and increase your chances of converting idle wishlist items into sales.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Encourage subscribers to create wishlists on your online store.</li><li>Remind them occasionally about their wishlist items.</li><li>Add an exclusive wishlist discount code to increase conversions.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Recommend Products Based on Abandoned Cart Items</strong></h2>



<p>If a visitor abandons their cart without making a purchase, itâ€™s your responsibility to follow up and offer solutions to your potential customers.<br></p>



<p>At this stage, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">abandoned cart emails</a> are the perfect opportunity to trigger a purchasing decision and recover otherwise-lost sales. A complicated checkout process or a simple distraction might easily cause cart abandonment, <em>but what if the product isnâ€™t right?</em><br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s why <a href="https://www.birchbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Birchbox</a> sends cart abandonment emails (with a twist):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="581" height="703" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email.png" alt="Birchbox Abandoned Cart Email" class="wp-image-88100" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email.png 581w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-248x300.png 248w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-380x460.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-29x35.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-41x50.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-405x490.png 405w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-220x266.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Abandoned-Cart-Email-385x466.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 581px) 100vw, 581px" /></figure></div>



<p>Birchbox reminds me of my abandoned items and tries to solve the problem that may be lying behind my cart abandonment.<br></p>



<p>Maybe, in their eyes, this wasnâ€™t exactly what I was looking forâ€¦<br></p>



<p>So, the email continues:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="553" height="587" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation.png" alt="Birchbox Product Recommendation" class="wp-image-88104" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation.png 553w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-283x300.png 283w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-380x403.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-47x50.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-462x490.png 462w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-220x234.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Birchbox-Product-Recommendation-385x409.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 553px) 100vw, 553px" /></figure></div>



<p>Thatâ€™s why the company offers me similar products that I might like more. More, they use social proof multiple times to make the recommendation stronger.<br></p>



<p>Notice how they include product ratings and reviews under each item. Thatâ€™s a well-thought use of customer feedback in emails, which Iâ€™ll return to in a moment.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Add a product recommendation section to your abandoned cart emails.</li><li>Recommend relevant and/or top-rated products.&nbsp;</li><li>Support your recommendations with customer feedback.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="8"><strong>8. Recover Lost Sales with an Abandoned Cart Email Flow</strong></h2>



<p>If youâ€™ve ever written an abandoned cart email, you likely know the struggle: you want to convince prospects to complete their purchase, but you donâ€™t want to sound too salesy. After all, failing to nudge MoFu leads towards the bottom of the funnel will likely result in them leaving, never to return.<br></p>



<p>Luckily, <a href="http://tuftandneedle.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Tuft &amp; Needle</a> has the perfect solution for you. Rather than promote the items you abandoned earlier, they get to the root of your problem with a three-part abandoned cart email flow.<br></p>



<p>When you abandon your cart on their website, Tuft &amp; Needle sends you, first, this email with the subject line â€œThe Spookiest Bed Time Story Everâ€¦â€<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="492" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-492x1024.png" alt="Tuft and Needle Abandoned Cart Email 1" class="wp-image-88188" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-492x1024.png 492w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-144x300.png 144w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-380x791.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-600x1248.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-17x35.png 17w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-24x50.png 24w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-235x490.png 235w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-220x458.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1-385x801.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-1.png 632w" sizes="(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px" /></figure></div>



<p>In <em>Part One</em> of their email flow, Tuft &amp; Needle agrees with prospects on one critical issue: mattress shopping sucks. After this honest statement, the company positions itself as the leading mattress e-tailer and warns you by saying, â€œDonâ€™t buy a mattress without reading this first.â€<br></p>



<p>When you click the hyperlink, you land on a page where Tuft &amp; Needle handles your objections and supports its claims with customer testimonials.<br></p>



<p>The second part of the flow arrives a few days later with the intriguing subject, â€œWhat Are You Paying For?â€<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="400" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-400x1024.png" alt="Tuft and Needle Abandoned Cart Email 2" class="wp-image-88192" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-400x1024.png 400w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-117x300.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-380x974.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-600x1538.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-14x35.png 14w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-20x50.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-191x490.png 191w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-220x564.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2-385x987.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-2.png 634w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, Tuft &amp; Needle, again, takes a consumer standpoint to mattress shopping and highlights its fair pricing.<br></p>



<p>Clicking the sentence, â€œWe made this page to prove we have nothing to hideâ€ takes you to another landing page, on which the company compares itself with its direct competitors, such as <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/casper-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Casper</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="456" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-1024x456.png" alt="Tuft and Needle Landing Page 2" class="wp-image-88204" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-1024x456.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-300x134.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-768x342.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-1536x684.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-760x338.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-1440x641.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-740x329.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2-385x171.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Landing-Page-2.png 1844w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As the final part of this well-thought flow, you get this email with the subject line, â€œYou Should Sleep on Big Decisions,â€ which is hard to disagree with:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="458" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-458x1024.png" alt="Tuft and Needle Abandoned Cart Email 3" class="wp-image-88196" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-458x1024.png 458w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-134x300.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-380x850.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-600x1341.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-16x35.png 16w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-22x50.png 22w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-219x490.png 219w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-220x492.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3-385x861.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tuft-and-Needle-Abandoned-Cart-Email-3.png 641w" sizes="(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px" /></figure></div>



<p>Maintaining its understanding tone, Tuft &amp; Needle makes a final attempt to persuade you by focusing on their 100-nights <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/satisfaction-guarantees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">satisfaction guarantee</a>.<br></p>



<p>While doing all these, notice that the company always keeps the CTA, â€œGo to Cartâ€ at the bottom of the email, in case they already persuaded you.<br></p>



<p>Even if prospects donâ€™t buy the abandoned product, with these three emails, Tuft &amp; Needle nurtures MoFu leads and prepares them for the next stage.<br></p>



<p>Itâ€™s an exceptional abandoned cart email flow, demonstrating how you can sell without being salesy.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Handle any possible objections in prospectsâ€™ minds, whether theyâ€™re about pricing, product quality, or delivery options.</li><li>Focus on how <em>different </em>you are to your competitors.</li><li>Resolve any questions by reminding your satisfaction guarantee.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2><strong>Part 3: BoFu Strategies</strong></h2>



<p>Bottom-of-the-funnel (BoFu) is the last stage of your sales funnel, where prospects are ready to become first-time buyers or repeat customers. At this stage, you need to make the process easier for your prospects leads and nudge them towards buying with the right incentives at the right time.<br></p>



<p>Here are five solid, yet underused strategies you can use to support your BoFu efforts.<br></p>





<h2 id="9"><strong>9. Use Customer Testimonials in Email</strong></h2>



<p>Customer testimonials are huge drivers of e-commerce sales. When used right, they add social proof to your business and help visitors overcome objections.<br></p>



<p>Many e-commerce brands display their customer reviews on homepages, landing pages, or product pages. But itâ€™s only exceptional brands that incorporate testimonials in their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/best-email-marketing-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email marketing</a>.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s an example by <a href="https://www.brooklinen.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Brooklinen</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="661" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email.png" alt="Brooklinen Customer Testimonial Email" class="wp-image-88108" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-270x300.png 270w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-380x422.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-441x490.png 441w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-220x244.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Customer-Testimonial-Email-385x428.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<p>Knowing the persuasive impact of testimonials, Brooklinen dedicates this email to display their top customer reviews. Another clever way of using customer testimonials in email marketing is to integrate it into your promotional emails.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://www.firebox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Firebox</a> does that:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="499" height="701" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email.png" alt="Firebox Customer Reviews Email" class="wp-image-88148" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email.png 499w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-214x300.png 214w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-380x534.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-36x50.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-349x490.png 349w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-220x309.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Customer-Reviews-Email-385x541.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px" /></figure></div>



<p>Rather than writing long <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-descriptions" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">descriptions</a>, Firebox uses customer reviews to let the products speak for themselves. After all, who else can describe a product better than an actual user?<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.violetgrey.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Violet Grey</a> takes it even one step further and carries customer testimonials to their subject lines:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="152" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-1024x152.png" alt="Violet Grey Customer Testimonial Subject Line" class="wp-image-88212" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-1024x152.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-300x45.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-768x114.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-380x56.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-600x89.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-760x113.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-180x27.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-740x110.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-220x33.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line-385x57.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Violet-Grey-Customer-Testimonial-Subject-Line.png 1293w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This way, the company creates social proof even before you open the email. Whatâ€™s more, by using a strong statement, they evoke your curiosity and make you want to see the product immediately.<br></p>



<p>Similar to Brooklinen, you can handpick your favorite testimonials about your product, service, or company, and send out occasional emails to spread the love. And if you donâ€™t have a large backlog of customer reviews yet, you can try including a few examples in your promotional emails.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items&nbsp;</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Pick 5 to 10 customer testimonials from your website.</li><li>Add customer feedback and ratings to your promotional emails.</li><li>Include product image, product link, and price information.</li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="10"><strong>10. Convince On-the-Fence Prospects</strong></h2>



<p>Not all bottom-funnel prospects stand at an equal distance to your checkout. Some might have concerns about your delivery options, whereas others might need a payment reminder.<br></p>



<p>At this stage, you should identify possible obstacles to buying and remove them with timely intervention.<br></p>



<p>When you begin your subscription process on <a href="https://www.barkbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Barkbox</a>, you walk through a few steps, asking information about your dog and its preferences. Before you choose a plan and proceed to checkout, you see this page:<br></p>



