<p>On it, Barkbox reminds you of their satisfaction guarantee, which they call â€œScoutâ€™s Honorâ€”<em>Ruv it or leave it guarantee.â€ </em>And below their guarantee icon, they use a dynamic text thatâ€™s updated with your dogâ€™s name to create a personal feeling.<br></p>



