<p>With a timely website popup that shows only on cart pages, you can inform prospects about your payment options and help them make a quick decisionâ€”just like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/success-stories/kings-queens" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Kings &amp; Queens</a> does:<br></p>



