<p>When an item in my wishlist goes out of stock, the â€œMove to Bagâ€ button changes to â€œSee Similar Items.â€<br></p>



<p>ASOS doesnâ€™t use an out-of-stock alert system, but the company found a way to keep customers engaged on sold-out product pages and increase their likelihood to convert.<br></p>



