<h2 id="12"><strong>12. Combine FOMO with Free Shipping</strong></h2>



<p>Itâ€™s no secret that free shipping is a highly effective incentive for completing a purchase. According to one study, <a href="https://www.invespcro.com/blog/free-shipping/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">93% of online shoppers buy more items</a>, when thereâ€™s a free shipping option. More, free shipping not only encourage visitors to complete the purchaseâ€”but it also helps you sell more.<br></p>



<p>By triggering prospectsâ€™ <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/fomo-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">fear-of-missing-out</a> (FOMO), you can nudge them to spend more and qualify for free shipping.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at how ASOS uses this strategy during checkout:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="927" height="396" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4.png" alt="Checkout Form" class="wp-image-88220" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4.png 927w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-300x128.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-768x328.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-380x162.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-600x256.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-760x325.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-740x316.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image26-4-385x164.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 927px) 100vw, 927px" /></figure></div>



<p>Right when I was about to place my order, I got this gentle free shipping reminder. And naturally, I spent 3,20 Danish Crowns (which is less than 50 cents) to get free shipping. (In fact, I spent even more.)<br></p>



<p>Itâ€™s because ASOS triggered my <em>FOMO</em>, and I didnâ€™t want to miss out on free shipping over 50 cents.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>If you want to nudge your bottom-funnel prospects to spend more, you can recommend products they can quickly add to their carts:</p>


