<h2 id="13"><strong>13. Ask for Referrals at the Right Time</strong></h2>



<p>In the ideal world of word-of-mouth marketing, your happy customers would automatically bring you new prospects that only heard the best things about your brand.<br></p>



<p>But thatâ€™s not how it is in real life.<br></p>



<p>With well-timed emails and the right incentives, you can encourage referrals and make your BoFu prospects bring you targeted ToFu leads.<br></p>



<p>Beardbrand knows the power of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/referral-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">referral marketing</a>. Thatâ€™s why a few days after placing an order, they send you this email with the subject line â€œYour friends will thank youâ€:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="995" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email.png" alt="Beardbrand Referral Email" class="wp-image-88080" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-211x300.png 211w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-380x540.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-600x853.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-345x490.png 345w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-220x313.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-385x547.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>With it, the company, first, confirms your decision to buy a Beardbrand product. Next, they offer you the opportunity to become a â€œgrooming guruâ€ and impress your friends.<br></p>



<p>When you refer, â€œa buddy,â€ your friend gets a special deal for their first order, and you become an expert in their eyes. Win. Win.<br></p>



<p>Shortly after I filled out Beardbrandâ€™s referral form, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/author/rikkethomsen" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Rikke</a> got this email:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="675" height="958" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program.png" alt="Beardbrand Referral Program" class="wp-image-88084" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program.png 675w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-211x300.png 211w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-380x539.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-600x852.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-345x490.png 345w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-220x312.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-385x546.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, Beardbrand offers her 25$ worth of store credit (because sheâ€™s, to her surprise, a lucky man.) But the discount code only applies to their starter kit. If Rikke buys the starter kit, Beardbrand will offer her another $25 credit, and sheâ€™ll be hooked.<br></p>



<p>This is a smart referral marketing strategy because it gives new prospects not only an incentive but also a place to use it.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Items</strong></h3>





<ul><li>Send out a referral email a few days after a customer receives their order.</li><li>Write the benefit of referral for both parties clearly.</li><li>Provide your new prospects a unique discount code that only applies to certain products.</li></ul>
</div></div>




