<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Limited-Time Offers</strong></h2>



<p>Whether itâ€™s a discount code or free shipping youâ€™re offering, limiting your incentive with time helps you convert more prospects into customers for a few reasons:<br></p>



<ul><li>Limited-time offers drive a sense of urgency and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity</a> of availability; and</li><li>They trigger consumersâ€™ <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/fomo-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">fear-of-missing-out</a> (FOMO).</li></ul>



<p>There are many different ways you can use limited-time offers in your emails and on your site, and here are three of its best examples.<br></p>





<h3><strong>i. Limited-Time Discounts</strong></h3>



<p>If youâ€™re running a limited-time sales campaign, you want to ensure that as many prospects as possible know about it.<br></p>



<p>Using on-site messages helps you achieve this goal by informing your site visitors about your time-sensitive offers.<br></p>



<p>Check out this example by <a href="https://www.puravidabracelets.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Pura Vida Bracelets</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="496" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-1024x496.png" alt="Pura Vida Bracelets Limited-Time Discount" class="wp-image-87849" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-1024x496.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-1536x744.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-1440x697.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pura-Vida-Bracelets-Limited-Time-Discount.png 1902w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>With this <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">exit-intent popup</a>, the company offers 15% off your next order with the goal of converting you into a customer.<br></p>



<p>Unlike many online stores that rely on discount codes, Pura Vida knows the influence of limited-time offers on hesitant visitors. Thatâ€™s why they add a countdown timer to their popup and invite you to make a quick decision by driving urgency.<br></p>





<h3><strong>ii. Limited-Time Free Shipping</strong></h3>



<p>While many marketers immediately think of discounts when they plan sales campaigns, some brands knows that free shipping is a more powerful incentive.<br></p>



<p>Yet, only a handful of them combine free shipping with limited-time offers.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.vinomofo.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Vinomofo</a> is one of those brands:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="266" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-1024x266.png" alt="Vinomofo Subject Line" class="wp-image-87873" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-1024x266.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-300x78.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-768x200.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-380x99.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-600x156.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-760x198.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-135x35.png 135w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-192x50.png 192w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-740x192.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-220x57.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line-385x100.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Subject-Line.png 1169w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>With this personalized <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">subject line</a> addressed to Rikke, Vinomofo promotes their offer clearly and makes you want to open their email.<br></p>



<p>Then, you discover that the company is running a flash sale campaign with free shipping, but only for a certain time:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="596" height="902" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Vinomofo-Flash-Sale-Email-1.gif" alt="Vinomofo Flash Sale Email" class="wp-image-87869"/></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Notice how Vinomofo drives a feeling of urgency by cleverly using a GIF.</em></p>





<p>To engage your site visitors and promote your free shipping offer, you can create a popup that shows only on your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product pages</a>. Lastly, donâ€™t forget to drive urgency with a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/countdown-timer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">countdown timer</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="760" height="680" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Free-Shipping-Popup-Example.gif" alt="Free Shipping Popup Example" class="wp-image-87817"/></figure></div>



<p>(ProTip: Add GIFs to your popups to make them eye-catching.)<br></p>





<h3><strong>iii. Limited-Time Freebies</strong></h3>



<p>While â€œ10% offâ€ might prompt some users to take action, itâ€™s harder to resist the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/words-that-sell" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">highly persuasive</a> power word â€œfree.â€<br></p>



<p>Furthermore, we know from our customersâ€™ experience that physical products outperform discount codes as incentives.<br></p>



<p>Combining the two, â€œfree productsâ€ work like a charm to convince on-the-fence prospects.<br></p>



<p>Although offering free products is an effective customer activation strategy, itâ€™s not feasible in the long term.<br></p>



<p>Instead of decreasing your profits and reducing your productsâ€™ <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/perceived-value" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">perceived value</a>, run a limited-time campaign where you offer free products and promote it on your site.<br></p>



<p>Just as <a href="https://barkbox.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">BarkBox</a> does:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="353" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-1024x353.png" alt="BarkBox Limited Time Popup" class="wp-image-87797" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-1024x353.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-768x264.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-380x131.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-600x207.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-760x262.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-145x50.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-740x255.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1-385x133.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Popup-1.png 1374w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Add a countdown timer to enhance your popup and hide it from your logged-in customers, using our <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/sitedata" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SiteData condition</a>.<br></p>



