<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Daily Deals</strong></h2>



<p>One brilliant sales promotion technique that creates excitement among consumers is daily deals.<br></p>



<p>Despite its effectiveness in converting prospects into customers, most companies, understandably, cannot afford to offer a new deal every day.<br></p>



<p>If you want to use daily deals as part of your sales promotion strategy, try combining it with your holiday campaigns.<br></p>



<p>While you can find an excuse to run a daily deal campaign at any time of the year, December is the perfect time for it, in my opinion.<br></p>



<p>Many companies already leverage the days leading up to Christmas by selling advent calendars with their products. While the advent calendar strategy works for physical products, it can easily help achieve your online conversion goals, too.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://poopourri.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Poo~Pourri</a> knows this well. Thatâ€™s why they offer six different deals over 12 days before Christmas and promote them in their emails:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="598" height="946" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Daily-Deals-Email.gif" alt="Poo Pourri Daily Deals Email" class="wp-image-87841"/></figure></div>



<p>With a sales campaign they call â€œ12 Days of Spritzmas,â€ the company emails you with a new deal every other day, ranging from special discounts to product bundles:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="774" height="711" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day.png" alt="Poo Pourri Deal of the Day" class="wp-image-87845" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day.png 774w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-300x276.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-768x705.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-380x349.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-600x551.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-760x698.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-38x35.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-54x50.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-533x490.png 533w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-220x202.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Poo-Pourri-Deal-of-the-Day-385x354.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px" /></figure></div>



<p>Poo~Pourri creates a curiosity gap and, as a result, you check your inbox the next day to learn about their new surprise offer. Because you know if you donâ€™t grab a daily deal, it will be gone forever (read: <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity</a>).<br></p>



<p>If youâ€™re wondering how you can apply this strategy on your site, <a href="https://www.cchobby.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Creativ Company</a> has the answer for you:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="358" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign.png" alt="Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign" class="wp-image-87809" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-300x105.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-768x269.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-380x133.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-600x210.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-760x266.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-100x35.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-143x50.png 143w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-740x259.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-220x77.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creativ_Company_Christmas_Calendar_Campaign-385x135.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In this advent calendar popup, Creativ Company asks you to open a new door every day to reveal the offer of the day, for 24 days until Christmas.<br></p>



<p>This way, the company successfully applies the idea of advent calendars to their website popups.<br></p>



<p>Itâ€™s a brilliant on-site sales promotion technique that builds anticipation and creates mystery during the holiday season.<br></p>



<p>Plus, you can create and set your campaigns long before Christmas with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/advanced-scheduling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Advanced Scheduling</a>.<br></p>



