<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Mystery Offers</strong></h2>



<p>While advent calendars are one way to evoke curiosity with your sales campaigns, mystery offers help engage your prospects all year round.<br></p>



<p>Building on the suspense of a surprise offer, you can make your sales campaigns more attention-grabbing by hiding the incentive.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at how <a href="https://www.ae.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">American Eagle</a> uses mystery offers in their email marketing:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="211" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-1024x211.png" alt="American Eagle Subject Line" class="wp-image-87785" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-1024x211.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-300x62.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-768x158.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-380x78.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-600x124.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-760x157.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-170x35.png 170w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-243x50.png 243w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-740x153.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-220x45.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line-385x79.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Subject-Line.png 1426w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>With this subject line, the company openly states whatâ€™s waiting for you inside, yet, they keep the offer a secret.<br></p>



<p>And in the email body, they build further anticipation:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="686" height="1005" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer.png" alt="American Eagle Mystery Offer" class="wp-image-87781" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer.png 686w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-205x300.png 205w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-380x557.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-600x879.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-24x35.png 24w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-34x50.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-334x490.png 334w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-220x322.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Mystery-Offer-385x564.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 686px) 100vw, 686px" /></figure></div>



<p>American Eagle combines scarcity and exclusivity with their mystery deal, and sends you a discount code with an offer â€œyou can ONLY get here.â€<br></p>



<p>Notice the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> (CTA) button â€œReveal Your Offerâ€ and how it encapsulates the excitement of opening a present.<br></p>



<p>Another company that uses mystery in their emails is <a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Chubbies</a>. However, rather than hiding the discount, Chubbies incorporates mystery into their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Black Friday campaign</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="793" height="987" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals.png" alt="Chubbies Black Friday Deals" class="wp-image-87805" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals.png 793w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-241x300.png 241w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-768x956.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-380x473.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-600x747.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-760x946.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-394x490.png 394w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-220x274.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Black-Friday-Deals-385x479.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 793px) 100vw, 793px" /></figure></div>



<p>Teasing their Black Friday deals, Chubbies uses blurred images of their new product line and creates mystery around them.<br></p>



<p>This is a smart sales promotion technique that works not only in email marketing but also in website popups.<br></p>



<p>Taking inspiration from Chubbies, you can promote your special deals or new arrivals with mystery products:</p>


