<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Cross-Sell Campaigns</strong></h2>



<p>Youâ€™re likely familiar with the following: You want to sell more while you got your visitorsâ€™ attention, but you donâ€™t want to scare them away by sounding too salesy.<br></p>



<p>With cross-sell campaigns, you can convert users who are at the decision stage of your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">sales funnel</a> with a higher <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/average-order-value" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">order value</a>.<br></p>



<p>How you frame your cross-sell campaigns, however, is the most critical step of this type of sales promotion.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.kikki-k.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">kikki.K</a> recently sent me this email with the subject line â€œ4th free, when you buy 3â€:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="796" height="956" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Email.gif" alt="kikki.K Email" class="wp-image-87829"/></figure></div>



<p>While â€œbuy 2, get 1 freeâ€ is the oldest sales promotion tactic in the book, kikki.K executes it successfully in their emails.<br></p>



<p>The company uses GIFs to spice up this otherwise boring <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/promotional-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">promotional email</a> and visually describes your gain from it:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="760" height="922" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kikki.K-Email-2.gif" alt="kikki.K Email 2" class="wp-image-87825"/></figure></div>



<p>Itâ€™s as easy as â€œ1, 2, 3, Free!â€<br></p>



<p>If you donâ€™t want to give your products away, free shipping is your best incentive option. And it works just as well in cross-sell campaigns.<br></p>



<p>Consumers are <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">willing to spend more</a> when free shipping is an option. This is a great chance to increase customersâ€™ average order value with relevant products.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://tartecosmetics.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Tarte</a> cleverly uses free shipping in their cross-sell campaigns. Check out this email they send with the subject line â€œ1 + 1 = Free shippingâ€:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="738" height="888" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Tarte-Email.gif" alt="Tarte Email" class="wp-image-87865"/></figure></div>



<p>If you want to qualify for free shipping, you need to combine these two products in your order.<br></p>



<p>The key to making this campaign work is to pick complementary products that are often bought together. Plus, you need to nudge users at the right time with website popups.<br></p>



<p>You can use our SiteData condition to trigger a popup and recommend complementary products when a visitor adds the first item to their cart:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="740" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-1024x740.png" alt="Cross-Sell Popup Example" class="wp-image-87813" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-1024x740.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-300x217.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-768x555.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-380x275.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-600x434.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-760x550.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-69x50.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-678x490.png 678w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-220x159.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example-385x278.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup-Example.png 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Itâ€™s a subtle yet effective nudge to increase your customersâ€™ order value with personalized <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">recommendations</a>.<br></p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Subscriber Specials</strong></h2>



<p>While <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">discounting</a> is an effective sales promotion strategy, you need to use it wisely.<br></p>



<p>Your long-time subscribers and first-time visitors have different needs, questions, and concerns. If you treat them the same way, you risk losing both.<br></p>



<p>Offer discounts to everyone and youâ€™ll reduce your productsâ€™ perceived value. But offer them to the right users at the right time and youâ€™ll have loyal customers.<br></p>



<p>Limiting your deals to email subscribers helps you reward your prospects when itâ€™s deserved and encourages them to become a customer.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.monki.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Monki</a> knows how to appreciate their subscribers. Take a look at this email they send to their email list:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="768" height="766" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale.gif" alt="Monki VIP Sale" class="wp-image-87837"/></figure></div>



<p>Framing their mid-season sale as â€œVIP Saleâ€ and inviting you to it, Monki creates an exclusive feeling in this email.<br></p>



<p>As you scroll down, they explain why you are a VIP and why you get this email:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="784" height="394" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2.png" alt="Monki VIP Sale 2" class="wp-image-87833" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2.png 784w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-300x151.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-768x386.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-380x191.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-600x302.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-760x382.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-99x50.png 99w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-740x372.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-220x111.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Monki-VIP-Sale-2-385x193.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 784px) 100vw, 784px" /></figure></div>



<p>Monki appreciates your decision to sign up for their newsletter and they reward you for it with early access to their mid-season sale.<br></p>



<p>An underused on-site sales promotion technique is to welcome returning visitors with a special offer.<br></p>



<p>And subscriber deals are the perfect example of it.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s a subscriber-only popup example you can use to inform subscribers about your next sale when they return to your site:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="926" height="836" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VIP-Sale-Popup-Example.gif" alt="VIP Sale Popup Example" class="wp-image-87877"/></figure></div>



<p>Make sure to use our â€œNewsletter Subscriberâ€ condition and your popup will only show to your existing subscribers.<br></p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Clearance Sales</strong></h2>



<p>Whether itâ€™s the end of the year or you need to make space in your inventory for a new product line, clearance sales are both online and offline retailersâ€™ favorite.<br></p>



<p>Itâ€™s a smart excuse to finish your stocks especially if youâ€™re selling seasonal products, such as winter clothing, pumpkin-themed candles, Christmas decorations, and so on.<br></p>



<p>Clearance sales are effective because consumers associate them with good bargain prices. Plus, it contains scarcity and urgency since the number of available items are limited.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.ae.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">American Eagle</a> uses this sales promotion technique in their emails. Check out this email they send with the subject line â€œUp to 70% off clearance: THIS. NEVER. HAPPENS.â€:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="624" height="812" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/American-Eagle-Email.gif" alt="American Eagle Email" class="wp-image-87777"/></figure></div>



<p>The company highlights the exclusivity and urgency of the deal by telling that the sale is â€œ3 days <strong>only</strong>â€ and â€œonline <strong>only</strong>.â€<br></p>



<p>Next, American Eagle invites you to buy these <em>last-chance </em>products before theyâ€™re <em>GONE.</em><br></p>



<p>Notice how the company uses scarcity to prompt you to take action as soon as possible.<br></p>



<p>Another company that runs clearance sales is <a href="https://factory.jcrew.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">J.Crew Factory</a> and they promote their campaign with the subject line â€œ1,000 clearance styles you just baaarely missed!â€:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="778" height="708" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/J.Crew-Factory-Clearance-Sale.gif" alt="J.Crew Factory Clearance Sale" class="wp-image-87821"/></figure></div>



<p>J.Crew Factory uses a specific number in the email to describe the extent of their sales campaign and openly triggers your FOMO.<br></p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Seasonal Deals</strong></h2>



<p>Itâ€™s not every day that you find an excuse to promote your products without coming off as salesy.<br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s why you need to leverage holidays and position your products as the best gift options on the market.<br></p>



<p>While itâ€™s difficult to get your prospectsâ€™ attention around Christmas or Black Friday, not all holidays are as busy.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://barkbox.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">BarkBox</a> uses National Dog Day as an excuse to offer seasonal deals:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="931" height="906" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email.png" alt="BarkBox Email" class="wp-image-87793" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email.png 931w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-300x292.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-768x747.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-380x370.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-600x584.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-760x740.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-36x35.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-51x50.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-504x490.png 504w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-220x214.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Email-385x375.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 931px) 100vw, 931px" /></figure></div>



