<p>On average, <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/439576/online-shopper-conversion-rate-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">only 2.42%</a> of e-commerce site visits convert into purchases.<br></p>



