<h2 id="Lush:-Educate-Your-Visitors-with-Content"><strong>1. Lush: Educate Your Visitors with Content</strong></h2>



<p>Thereâ€™s one thing you should always keep in mind when optimizing your product pages: everything you do has to be in line with your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">value proposition</a>.<br></p>



<p>Before starting, ask yourself what value you want to convey to your site visitors. Is it your fast shipping option, bulletproof <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/satisfaction-guarantees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">satisfaction guarantee</a>, broad product range, natural ingredients, or something else?<br></p>



<p>Knowing this well, <a href="http://lush.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Lush</a> builds their product pages around their nature-conscious products and fresh ingredients.<br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s why they add a detailed list of ingredients under their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-descriptions" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product descriptions</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="554" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-1024x554.png" alt="Lush Ingredient List" class="wp-image-76563" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-1024x554.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-300x162.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-768x415.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-380x205.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-600x324.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-760x411.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-740x400.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-220x119.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List-385x208.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Ingredient-List.png 1191w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The company both informs and educates site visitors about their products.<br></p>



<p>And the education goes further with their content.<br></p>



<p>When you scroll down the page, youâ€™ll see a â€œRelated Articleâ€ section:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="448" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-1024x448.png" alt="Lush Related Article" class="wp-image-76567" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-1024x448.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-768x336.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-600x263.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-760x333.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-114x50.png 114w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-740x324.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article-385x169.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Lush-Related-Article.png 1215w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In this example, the company explains transparently how and why they changed their product formula and educate the readers about their ingredients.<br></p>



<p>To further support their position as a conscious brand, they use <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/trust-badges" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">badges</a> and certifications, which resonate with their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/buyer-personas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">buyer persona</a>:<br></p>



