<p>Finally, Lush goes beyond classic product videos and greet visitors with a featured video showing the product in action:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="650" height="234" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Lush-Featured-Video.gif" alt="Lush Featured Video" class="wp-image-103626"/></figure></div>



<p>This way, the product becomes more concrete and easy-to-understand for their visitors.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul class="is-style-default"><li>Keep your product pages in line with your value proposition.</li><li>Write detailed and helpful product descriptions.</li><li>Educate your visitors with content and link to relevant content on product pages.</li><li>Use featured videos to show how to use your products.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Allbirds:-Collect-Warm-Leads-on-Product-Pages"><strong>2. Allbirds: Collect Warm Leads on Product Pages</strong></h2>



<p>We all want what we canâ€™t have.<br></p>



<p>A product suddenly becomes more attractive when itâ€™s no longer available. And the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity</a> of an item makes it more desirable.<br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s why <a href="https://www.allbirds.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Allbirds</a> differentiates between their classics and limited edition items and highlights the scarcity of the latter:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="680" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-1024x680.png" alt="Allbirds Product Page" class="wp-image-76443" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-1024x680.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-300x200.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-768x510.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-380x252.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-600x398.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-760x504.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-53x35.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-75x50.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-738x490.png 738w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-220x146.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page-385x256.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Page.png 1029w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>To help site visitors better understand their products, the company offers a size chart that opens on the same page. This way, they prevent the risk of losing the visitor on a new tab.<br></p>



<p>Allbirds removes the barriers to purchase by offering more than one payment option on their site. And visitors can see those options before going to the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">checkout page</a>.<br></p>



<p>In addition to displaying the product from multiple angles, the company also uses a model video to show how the shoes look and feel when you walk in them:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="618" height="588" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Product-Video.gif" alt="Allbirds Product Video" class="wp-image-76447"/></figure></div>



<p>Scrolling further down the page, you see a section dedicated to user-generated content that shows the products in real life:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="389" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-1024x389.png" alt="Allbirds User Generated Content" class="wp-image-76451" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-1024x389.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-300x114.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-768x292.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-380x145.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-600x228.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-760x289.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-92x35.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-131x50.png 131w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-740x281.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content-385x146.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-User-Generated-Content.png 1212w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Finally, Allbirds uses out-of-stock notifications to grow their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email list</a> with warm leads:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="978" height="843" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications.png" alt="Allbirds Out of Stock Notifications" class="wp-image-76439" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications.png 978w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-300x259.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-768x662.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-380x328.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-600x517.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-760x655.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-568x490.png 568w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-220x190.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Allbirds-Out-of-Stock-Notifications-385x332.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 978px) 100vw, 978px" /></figure></div>



<p>In addition to notifying you when the item is back in stock, they also ask if youâ€™d like to join their email list. Yet, they do it with a value-driven copy (â€œLet me know about new products, colors too.â€) and a pre-selected checkbox.<br></p>



<p>This way, the company collects highly interested leads that they can target with personalized email campaigns.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>If youâ€™re selling products <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">limited by time</a> or stock, make them stand out on your product pages.</li><li>Offer charts and guides that open on the same page.</li><li>Consider adding multiple payment options to your e-commerce site.</li><li>Use product videos to show the item in action.</li><li>Curate user-generated content with a third-party app, such as <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="http://www.olapic.com/" target="_blank">Olapic</a> or <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://www.curalate.com/" target="_blank">Curalate</a>.</li><li>Implement out-of-stock alerts and ask users for permission to add them to your email list.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Away:-Explain-Product-Options-in-Detail"><strong>3. Away: Explain Product Options in Detail</strong></h2>



<p>How do you understand if a product is worth checking out?<br></p>



<p>If youâ€™re like most of us, you look at the reviews it has.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/learn/local-consumer-review-survey/#Q2" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">According to one survey</a>, 91% of consumers trust reviews as much as recommendations from personal contacts.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://awaytravel.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Away</a> knows the importance of product reviews. Thatâ€™s why the average product rating and the number of reviews is the first thing you see when you visit one of their product pages:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="753" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-1024x753.png" alt="Away Product Page" class="wp-image-76467" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-1024x753.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-300x221.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-768x565.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-380x279.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-600x441.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-760x559.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-666x490.png 666w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-220x162.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1-385x283.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Page-1.png 1330w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When they offer two different product options (ejectable or without battery), they clarify what these terms mean to the reader.<br></p>



<p>Clicking the link â€œWhich one should I get?â€ opens a slide-in text and you can decide which option is best for you:<br></p>



