<p>Away doesnâ€™t only offer a Reviews section at the end of their product pages. They also allow visitors to ask product-related questions and display their answers in that section.<br></p>



<p>This way, they remove the visitorsâ€™ doubts and help them make better purchasing decisions.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Display product ratings under <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-headlines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product headlines</a>.</li><li>If youâ€™re offering different product options, explain them clearly.</li><li>Try hiding longer pieces of information to save up space.</li><li>Consider offering a personalization option for your products.</li><li>Recommend products that <em>really </em>complement the original item.</li><li>Allow visitors to ask questions on product pages and answer them as soon as possible.</li></ul>
</div></div>



