<p>Bestsellers gain legitimacy because they have the approval of past customers.<br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s exactly what <a href="https://www.bando.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Ban.do</a> tries to highlight on their product pages:<br></p>



