<p>They use the <em>bestseller </em>tag on both <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-listing-pages" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product listing</a> and detail pages to combine <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">social proof</a> with the fear of missing out (FOMO).<br></p>



