<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Use â€œbestseller,â€ â€œtrending,â€ or â€œselling fastâ€ tags on product pages to create social proof and a sense of urgency.</li><li>Consider implementing a third-party tool to allow customers to pay in installments.</li><li>Write product descriptions that align with your brandâ€™s voice.</li><li>Use a subtle tone to cross-sell without being salesy.</li><li>Offer free additions or refills that complement the product.</li><li>Show the faces of your employees and highlight their expertise within the field.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Brooklinen:-Reduce-Cart-Abandonment-with-Messenger"><strong>5. Brooklinen: Reduce Cart Abandonment with Messenger</strong></h2>



<p>As I wrote before, top e-commerce brands follow best practices AND add something extra.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at this product page by <a href="https://brooklinen.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Brooklinen</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="579" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-1024x579.png" alt="Brooklinen Product Page" class="wp-image-76519" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-1024x579.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-300x170.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-768x434.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-380x215.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-600x339.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-760x430.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-88x50.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-740x418.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page-385x218.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Brooklinen-Product-Page.png 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Similar to many other examples above, they display product ratings and the number of reviews.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Since they offer different weight options, they help you choose the best one without you having to leave the page.<br></p>



<p>Now that youâ€™re persuaded by the productâ€™s five-star rating and youâ€™ve easily made a choice between the two options, youâ€™re ready to add the item to your cart.<br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s when Brooklinen offers you the option to get cart updates on Facebook Messenger.<br></p>



<p>When you select that option, they send you a message shortly after:<br></p>



