<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Recover abandoned carts on Messenger with third-party tools, such as <a href="https://www.klaviyo.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Klaviyo</a> and <a href="https://octaneai.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Octane AI</a>.</li><li>Pick your best customer testimonials and display them separately on your product pages.</li><li>Invite visitors to ask you any questions before making a purchase.</li><li>Set up a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/product-demo/connect-with-visitors-time-triggered-sleekbox" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">time-triggered Connect with Visitors campaign</a> to assist visitors with a long on-site time.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Fabletics:-Evoke-Curiosity-to-Increase-Signups"><strong>6. Fabletics: Evoke Curiosity to Increase Signups</strong></h2>



<p>Price is <a href="https://www.bigcommerce.com/blog/omni-channel-retail/#why-us-consumers-shop-where-they-shop" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">among the top three reasons</a> why American consumers buy from a particular e-commerce site.<br></p>



<p>If youâ€™re offering better prices than your competitors, or, if you have discounted items on your online store, make sure your visitors are aware of it.<br></p>



<p>One way to highlight your price advantage is to contrast it with the original price.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://www.fabletics.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Fabletics</a> does it on their product pages:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="864" height="829" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price.png" alt="Fabletics VIP Price" class="wp-image-76535" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price.png 864w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-300x288.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-768x737.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-380x365.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-600x576.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-760x729.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-36x35.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-52x50.png 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-511x490.png 511w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-220x211.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fabletics-VIP-Price-385x369.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px" /></figure></div>



<p>Their â€œNew VIP Priceâ€ is discounted twice compared to the retail price. And it encourages visitors to consider buying the product (together with a VIP subscription.)<br></p>



<p>Even though companies try to display their products from as many angles as possible, it wonâ€™t look the same when two different people wear the same thing.<br></p>



<p>Thatâ€™s why Fabletics help you guess how their products might look on you with the option to choose different models:<br></p>



