<p>And if you want to see the products on <em>real </em>people, rather than only models, Fabletics curate customer photos under the model pictures.<br></p>



<p>When you move down to product recommendations, youâ€™ll see that the company hides some of the items which can be unlocked upon signing up:<br></p>



