<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Compare your discounted prices with full retail prices and focus on the savings.</li><li>Give visitors an expected delivery date.</li><li>Consider offering free returns and a price guarantee.</li><li>Make suggestions on how to make the most of your products.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Bellroy:-Help-Visitors-Make-Better-Decisions"><strong>9. Bellroy: Help Visitors Make Better Decisions</strong></h2>



<p>Online shopping carries a certain amount of risk for consumers.<br></p>



<p>They canâ€™t touch or try on products as they can in brick-and-mortar shops.<br></p>



<p>Luckily, many online stores have found a smart way around this and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/bellroy-marketing">Bellroy</a> is one of those companies:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="639" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-1024x639.png" alt="Bellroy Product Page" class="wp-image-76491" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-1024x639.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-768x479.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-600x374.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-760x474.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page-385x240.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Product-Page.png 1157w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The companyâ€™s goal is simple: They try to help you as much as possible so that you can make better-informed purchasing decisions.<br></p>



<p>They offer customers two size options based on their walletsâ€™ use cases.<br></p>



<p>Assuming that you wouldnâ€™t know the exact dimensions of your national currency, Bellroy helps you find the best option for you.<br></p>



<p>When you click the question mark symbol, a text pops up on the same page and gives you more information:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="816" height="574" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes.png" alt="Bellroy Wallet Sizes" class="wp-image-76499" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes.png 816w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-300x211.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-768x540.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-380x267.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-600x422.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-760x535.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-697x490.png 697w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-220x155.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Wallet-Sizes-385x271.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" /></figure></div>



<p>If youâ€™re still unsure, Bellroy invites you to contact them and theyâ€™ll be happy to help you out.<br></p>



<p>Bellroy also helps you picture the product better by using a size comparison tool:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="900" height="646" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1.png" alt="Bellroy Size Comparison Tool" class="wp-image-76495" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1.png 900w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-300x215.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-768x551.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-380x273.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-600x431.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-760x546.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-683x490.png 683w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-220x158.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Size-Comparison-Tool-1-385x276.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></figure></div>



<p>Using a third-party service, called <a href="https://tangiblee.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Tangiblee</a>, the company lets you compare the product with some of the items you might have lying around, such as an iPhone, a key, or a credit card.<br></p>



<p>Since customers can now picture the product in their minds, thereâ€™s a smaller likelihood that theyâ€™ll be disappointed when they receive it.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Guide your visitors to choose the best product option for them.</li><li>Explain the different options in detail by using real-life examples.</li><li>Ask visitors to reach out to you if they need further help in choosing a product.</li><li>Compare your product sizes with simple items or use a third-party tool, such as <a href="https://tangiblee.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Tangiblee</a>.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Missguided:-Cross-Sell-with-Complementary-Products"><strong>10. Missguided: Cross-Sell with Complementary Products</strong></h2>



<p>When a visitor lands on one of your product pages, it often means that theyâ€™re interested in your online store and considering buying from you.<br></p>



<p>A gentle nudge can move those visitors from consideration to the decision stage of your marketing funnel.<br></p>



<p>Often, persuasion triggers are the perfect nudge you need on product pages.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at this example by <a href="https://www.missguided.eu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Missguided</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="799" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-1024x799.png" alt="Missguided Product Page" class="wp-image-76575" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-1024x799.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-300x234.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-768x599.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-380x297.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-600x468.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-760x593.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-64x50.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-628x490.png 628w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-220x172.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page-385x300.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Product-Page.png 1057w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>They combine social proof with scarcity by adding labels on product images.<br></p>



<p>First, they affirm your interest in the product by saying â€œgood choiceâ€. Then, they support it with social proof by writing â€œseveral others are checking this out right now.â€<br></p>



<p>Although they donâ€™t directly tell you to hurry up, knowing that many others are viewing the product creates a sense of urgency without disturbing you.<br></p>



<p>Missguided aims to cross-sell on product pages through the â€œshop this lookâ€ option:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="941" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-1024x941.png" alt="Missguided Shop This Look" class="wp-image-76579" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-1024x941.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-300x276.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-768x706.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-380x349.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-600x551.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-760x698.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-38x35.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-54x50.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-533x490.png 533w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-220x202.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look-385x354.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Missguided-Shop-This-Look.png 1074w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you click the button, you can quickly view the other items the model is wearing and add them to your cart. And the best part is, you can do that without leaving the page.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Add persuasion triggers to product images.</li><li>Cross-sell complementary products without forcing visitors to leave the product page.</li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Forever-21:-Use-Customer-Feedback-in-Product-Descriptions"><strong>11. Forever 21: Use Customer Feedback in Product Descriptions</strong></h2>



<p>When youâ€™re writing <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-descriptions" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product descriptions</a> for your online store, you have an idea about your products.<br></p>



<p>You can guess how a sofa might look in an average living room or how a dress might fit an average person.<br></p>



<p>But <em>you</em> are not your customers.<br></p>



<p>In some cases, customer reviews can give you valuable insights about your products.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://www.forever21.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Forever 21</a> uses customer feedback on their product pages:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="765" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-1024x765.png" alt="Forever 21 Product Page" class="wp-image-76539" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-1024x765.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-300x224.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-768x574.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-380x284.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-600x449.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-760x568.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-656x490.png 656w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-220x164.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page-385x288.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Product-Page.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Under the color and size information, the company displays a dynamic â€œFit Ratingâ€ for their products. This way, their visitors know what to expect from the product so they can make more accurate decisions.<br></p>



<p>Whatâ€™s more, the rating is updated based on real customer reviews.<br></p>



<p>The company also lets you share the product on social media and via email in case you want to get a second opinion or make a suggestion.<br></p>



<p>After the basic product information, youâ€™ll see a short section with the headline â€œWhy did you choose this?â€:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="223" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-1024x223.png" alt="Forever 21 Reviews" class="wp-image-76543" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-1024x223.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-300x65.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-768x167.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-380x83.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-600x131.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-760x166.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-161x35.png 161w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-229x50.png 229w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-740x161.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-220x48.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews-385x84.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Forever-21-Reviews.png 1193w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Here they display quotes from real customers explaining why they bought the item in one sentence.<br></p>



<p>Itâ€™s a quick and simple way of collecting product reviews and using them to persuade potential customers.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaways</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<ul><li>Update your product descriptions based on customer reviews.</li><li>Add social sharing buttons to product pages.</li><li>Ask customers to write one or two words about why they chose that product.</li></ul>




</div></div>



<h2 id="Pandora:-Add-a-â€œHintâ€-Option-to-Product-Pages"><strong>12. Pandora: Add a â€œHintâ€ Option to Product Pages</strong></h2>



<p>Some purchases require more than one visit. And some decisions involve more than one person.<br></p>



<p>If youâ€™re selling <em>giftable </em>products on your e-commerce site, you should make it easy for your visitors to drop a hint to their friends and family.<br></p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://us.pandora.net" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Pandora</a> does that successfully:<br></p>



