<h2><strong>7 Proven Satisfaction Guarantee Examples</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. The Lifetime Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. The Free Trial Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. The First-Time Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. The Lowest Price Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. The Happiness Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. The Fun Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. The Branded Guarantee</a></p>





<h2 id="1"><strong>1. The Lifetime Guarantee</strong></h2>



<p>Your satisfaction guarantee tells visitors many things about your online store:&nbsp;</p>



<ul><li>How easy it is to return a product;&nbsp;</li><li>How good of customer service they should expect;</li><li>What happens if they regret buying that product;</li><li>and so on.</li></ul>



<p>But more importantly, it tells visitors how much <em>confidence </em>you have in your products.</p>



<p>And for consumers, it points to <em>product quality</em>.</p>



<p>Many brands limit themselves with 30-day or 90-day money back guarantees. And thatâ€™s only one way to go.</p>



<p>Offering a lifetime guarantee, on the other hand, is the ultimate level of confidence you can display.</p>



<p>When you frame your guarantee around a fixed number of days, you risk triggering a question in consumersâ€™ minds. If a product has a 30-day guarantee, it automatically puts the idea of returning the item <em>before the time runs out </em>into their minds.</p>



<p>A lifetime guarantee is a bold choice, but it eliminates the customersâ€™ urge to return products and creates a trust for your product quality.</p>



<p>Hereâ€™s how <a href="https://brooklinen.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Brooklinen</a> offers a lifetime guarantee on all their products:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="337" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-1024x337.png" alt="Brooklinen Lifetime Guarantee" class="wp-image-92085" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-1024x337.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-300x99.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-768x252.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-380x125.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-600x197.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-760x250.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-1440x473.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-106x35.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-152x50.png 152w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-740x243.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-220x72.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee-385x127.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Lifetime-Guarantee.png 1509w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The company phrases the guarantee in a way to explain how <em>proud </em>they are of their craftsmanship.</p>



<p>And if anything <em>ever </em>happens to your Brooklinen products, they offer free repairs or replacements.</p>



<p>You donâ€™t always have to offer a money back guarantee on your e-commerce site. Repairs, refills, or renewals are also effective promises you can make to your customers.</p>



<p>Most of your customers will never even ask for it, but a lifetime guarantee will put your brand in a strong position for customer satisfaction.</p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. The Free Trial Guarantee</strong></h2>



<p>Offering a free trial for a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">limited time</a> before selling a product or service is one of the oldest tricks in the book.</p>



<p>Marketers know that the free trial period is their chance to influence the consumer and get them hooked on the product.</p>



<p>If someone is already satisfied with the product during the trial period, chances are, theyâ€™ll be ready to pay the full price once itâ€™s over.</p>



<p>Even though itâ€™s highly effective in converting site visitors into customers, we tend to associate free trial with SaaS companies (just like ours.)</p>



<p>But free trials have great potential waiting to be explored by e-commerce sites.</p>



<p><a href="https://warbyparker.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Warby Parker</a> has already discovered that and their take on free trial guarantees is something to behold:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="413" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-1024x413.png" alt="Warby Parker Free Trial Guarantee" class="wp-image-92129" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-1024x413.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-300x121.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-768x310.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-380x153.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-600x242.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-760x307.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-1440x581.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-87x35.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-124x50.png 124w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-740x299.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-220x89.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Free-Trial-Guarantee-385x155.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-F