<p>The American online store for glasses offers visitors a different kind of free trial.</p>



<p>Knowing that shopping for glasses is a personal experience, the company goes beyond virtual try-ons and offers visitors a chance to try the products at homeâ€”for free.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="566" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-1024x566.png" alt="Warby Parker Try at Home" class="wp-image-92133" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-1024x566.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warby-Parker-Try-at-Home.png 1204w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you visit a product page that is part of the program, you see two options: â€œTry at home for freeâ€ and â€œBuy from $95â€.</p>



<p>You can choose up to five frames to try at home for free and find the one that fits your face perfectly.</p>



<p>Warby Parker offers both free shipping and free returns, only to make things easier for their customers.</p>



<p>If youâ€™re selling products that <em>have to</em> be a perfect fit for your customers, you can offer them alternatives for a limited period.</p>



<p>Customers will have a more pleasant shopping experience, make better decisions, and theyâ€™ll be more willing to buy the product when they know itâ€™s easy to try and see.</p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. The First-Time Guarantee</strong></h2>



<p>First impressions matter.</p>



<p>No matter what youâ€™re selling, the first purchase is your greatest chance to impress customers.</p>



<p>You need to make sure that first-time customers have an exceptional shopping experience so that you can convince them to buy from you again.</p>



<p>A powerful satisfaction guarantee not only turns visitors into customers. It also converts<em> first-timers</em> into <em>repeat buyers.</em></p>



<p>But what do you do if you canâ€™t offer a free trial guarantee on your e-commerce site?</p>



<p><strong>Offer a first-time guarantee instead.</strong></p>



<p><a href="https://mackweldon.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mack Weldon</a> is a brilliant example of first-time guarantees:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="372" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-1024x372.png" alt="Mack Weldon First Time Guarantee" class="wp-image-92101" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-1024x372.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-300x109.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-768x279.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-380x138.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-600x218.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-760x276.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-96x35.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-138x50.png 138w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-740x269.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-220x80.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee-385x140.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mack-Weldon-First-Time-Guarantee.png 1107w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Offering what they call a â€œtry on guarantee,â€ the company wants to ensure that customers are happy with the first purchase they make.</p>



<p>Since theyâ€™re selling underwear online, offering an exchange due to dissatisfaction is not an option for Mack Weldon.</p>



<p>So they find a better way to guarantee customer happiness, instead.</p>



<p>If you donâ€™t love the first pair of underwear you buy, they send you a different size, style, or issue a refund. And you get to keep the pair you tried on.&nbsp;</p>



<p>They aim to make a good first impression by ensuring product satisfaction. Plus, they increase your chances of making another purchase and becoming a repeat customer.</p>



