</div></figure>



<p>This is, by far, the most memorable way you can frame your guarantee.</p>



<p>Sunski offers a Lifetime Guarantee on their site, but with a little twist:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="887" height="338" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty.png" alt="Sunski Product Page Forever Warranty" class="wp-image-92125" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty.png 887w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-300x114.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-768x293.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-380x145.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-600x229.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-760x290.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-92x35.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-131x50.png 131w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-740x282.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Product-Page-Forever-Warranty-385x147.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 887px) 100vw, 887px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you visit a product page, you see this drawing that communicates the product guarantee.</p>



<p>Combined with the phrasing â€œ<em>forever </em>warrantyâ€ and the brilliant guarantee video, the company wins the customers with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/humor-in-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">humor</a>.</p>



<p>No matter which type of warranty youâ€™re offering, try bringing some joy into your guarantee pages and youâ€™ll start making more out of them.</p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. The Branded Guarantee</strong></h2>



<p>Consumers are now immune to generic guarantees that say <em>â€œIf youâ€™re not satisfied with our product, return it within 30 days.â€</em></p>



<p>They donâ€™t even notice it, let alone be persuaded by it.</p>



<p>As the Sunski example above proves, satisfaction guarantees donâ€™t have to be yet another legal, must-have page on your site.</p>



<p>After all, the purpose is to reassure your site visitors and nudge them to make an easier buying decision.</p>



<p>The more interesting your guarantee is, the more attention it will catch. And that means better chances of convincing and converting site visitors into customers.</p>



<p>This doesnâ€™t mean that you have to write a song about your refund policy, too (although I strongly support the idea.)</p>



<p>Find a way to <em>own </em>your satisfaction guarantee and align it with your brand voice.</p>



<p>Just like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/casper-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Casper</a> does it:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="959" height="504" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee.png" alt="Casper Satisfaction Guarantee" class="wp-image-92089" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee.png 959w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-300x158.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-768x404.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-380x200.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-600x315.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-760x399.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-740x389.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-220x116.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Satisfaction-Guarantee-385x202.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 959px) 100vw, 959px" /></figure></div>



<p>Instead of calling it a 100-day-warranty, the famous mattress company phrases their guarantee as a <em>100-Nights Trial Period</em>.</p>



<p>They <em>brand </em>the guarantee in a way that is highly relevant to their products and in a humorous tone.</p>



<p>If youâ€™re unsure about what type of guarantee to offer on your online store, think about the worries of your customers: Why might they want to return the product? Which potential problems can occur after the purchase and make them change their minds?</p>



<p>Selling mattresses-in-a-box, Casper knows that customers wonâ€™t be willing to pack the product to return it, so they guarantee that theyâ€™ll pick it up for you.</p>



<p>Theyâ€™re also well aware that customers probably wonâ€™t change their minds after sleeping on a mattress for three months.</p>



<p>But <em>if </em>that happens, they know that Casper will be there for them. And thatâ€™s the whole point of satisfaction guarantees.</p>



