<h2><strong>What Is an Order Confirmation Email?</strong></h2>



<p>An order confirmation email is a transactional email informing customers that you received and/or processed their order.</p>



<p>Order confirmation emails contain important transaction details, such as delivery address, items purchased, amount paid, and more.</p>



<p>However, when used right, an order confirmation email is much more than a receipt.</p>



<p>Itâ€™s the first step in turning one-time buyers into repeat customers, and repeat customers into brand advocates.</p>



<p>A good order confirmation email captures the buyerâ€™s excitement, eliminates confusion, and, more importantly, builds the foundations of a fruitful relationship with your customers.</p>



<p>Letâ€™s see how in seven simple steps.</p>





<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Give the Three Wâ€™s</strong></h2>



<p>Although hitting the â€œPlace Your Orderâ€ button creates joy and excitement for manyâ€¦</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="337" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Excited-Rikke.gif" alt="Excited Rikke" class="wp-image-92316"/></figure></div>



<p>â€¦this is not always the case for your customers.</p>



<p>Regardless of a well-thought <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">checkout process</a> or multiple <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/trust-badges" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">trust badges</a>, online shopping always carries uncertainty. Some customers will experience post-purchase excitement, whereas others will feel uneasy.</p>



<p>The good news is you can address both emotions in your confirmation emails and turn them to your advantage.</p>



<p>Itâ€™s no secret that giving detailed information is crucial when putting your customersâ€™ minds at ease after they place an order.</p>



<p>However, the key is giving them â€œthe three wâ€™sâ€<em> </em>of their order in a clear, easily understandable way: <em>where, when, and what.</em></p>



<p><a href="https://www.asos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ASOS</a> is the best example of well-written order confirmation emails:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="583" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-583x1024.png" alt="ASOS Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92276" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-583x1024.png 583w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-171x300.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x667.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x1054.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-20x35.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-28x50.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-279x490.png 279w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x386.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x676.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 750w" sizes="(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you make a purchase, you get an automated email with your order details, under three headings: <em>where, when, </em>and <em>what you ordered.</em></p>



<p>Everything you need to know is in this email, from your delivery address to the expected arrival date. You also get a short order summary with the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-descriptions" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">productâ€™s description</a>, size, quantity, and price information, as well as the chosen payment method.</p>



<p>Knowing that returns and refunds are costly and time-consuming, ASOS gives you the option to cancel your order if youâ€™re hesitant, under a headline that reads â€œChanged your mind?â€</p>



<p>Whatâ€™s more, ASOS relieves you by reminding you of their flexible return policy. This way, ASOS guarantees <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/satisfaction-guarantees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">customer satisfaction</a> from the first email and reduces any unease with shopping online.</p>



<p>In the remainder of the email, the company encourages you to join their newsletter, engage with their content, and download their mobile app:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="750" height="661" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2.png" alt="ASOS Order Confirmation Email 2" class="wp-image-92272" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2.png 750w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-300x264.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-380x335.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-600x529.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-40x35.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-57x50.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-556x490.png 556w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-220x194.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-385x339.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></figure></div>



<p>ASOS knows what its customers expect from this email. Thatâ€™s why any self-promotion only comes after you get the crucial information, in case you â€œwant more ASOS.â€</p>



<p>While transactional emails are a good place to promote your brand, always focus on the three wâ€™s, first.</p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Set Expectations</strong></h2>



<p>While order confirmation emails act as receipts of purchases, thatâ€™s only the beginning of their purposes.</p>



<p>By informing customers about the next steps, order confirmation emails also help you set expectations.</p>



<p>Check out this example by <a href="http://bestseller.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Bestseller</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="593" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-593x1024.png" alt="Bestseller Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92300" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-593x1024.png 593w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-174x300.png 174w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-768x1326.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-890x1536.png 890w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x656.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x1036.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-760x1312.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-20x35.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-29x50.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-284x490.png 284w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x380.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x665.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 917w" sizes="(max-width: 593px) 100vw, 593px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you place an order and get a confirmation email from Bestseller, you see a progress bar with three icons on top. Thanks to this visual aid and the section called â€œWhatâ€™s Nextâ€ below, you know what to expect about your order over the next few days.</p>



<p>Bestseller knows that you might have some questions about your order. Thatâ€™s why the second headline you see in this email is â€œNeed Help?â€</p>



<p>After providing you with the transactional details (read: three wâ€™s), Bestseller invites you to sign up for their newsletter. Since customers already committed to something bigger, itâ€™s a good time to ask for a smaller favor.</p>



<p>Similar to many successful e-tailers, Bestseller sends a delivery confirmation email when it ships your items:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="959" height="910" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2.png" alt="Bestseller Order Confirmation Email 2" class="wp-image-92296" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2.png 959w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-300x285.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-768x729.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-380x361.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-600x569.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-760x721.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-516x490.png 516w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-220x209.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bestseller-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-385x365.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 959px) 100vw, 959px" /></figure></div>



<p>Much like the first email, the company sets expectations with a progress bar thatâ€™s now moved one step further.</p>



<p>The â€œWhatâ€™s Nextâ€ section has now changed to include shipping information so that you can track your order and look forward to receiving it.</p>



<p>Note that the â€œNeed Help?â€ section is still at the top of the email because the order process hasnâ€™t completed yet.</p>



<p>Remember to make it easy for customers to reach out to you at any stage of their order. Otherwise, youâ€™ll end up with confused customers, or worse, lose them to a competitor.</p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Guide Your Customers</strong></h2>



<p>You gave practical information and set expectations about the process. What comes next?</p>



<p>There are two options:&nbsp;</p>



<ul><li>You can let your customers close the confirmation email and get back to their lives; or</li><li>You can keep them engaged with your brand and stay top of mind.</li></ul>



<p>Assuming you would also choose the second option, Iâ€™ll show how you can guide your customers in the right direction with an engaging order confirmation email example.</p>



<p>When you buy something from <a href="https://www.cultbeauty.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Cult Beauty</a>, this is the confirmation email you get:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="537" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-537x1024.png" alt="Cult Beauty Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92312" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-537x1024.png 537w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-157x300.png 157w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x725.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x1145.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-18x35.png 18w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-26x50.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-257x490.png 257w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x420.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x735.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cult-Beauty-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 687w" sizes="(max-width: 537px) 100vw, 537px" /></figure></div>



<p>Following best practices, Cult Beauty captures your excitement with its headline. Then, it gives you the details of your transaction.</p>



<p>But something more interesting is happening on the right side of the email.</p>



<p>After offering you a helping hand, Cult Beauty invites you back to its site, but with three different options:</p>



<ul><li>Update your preferences and get a discount on your next order (read: data enrichment and segmentation);</li><li>Check out whatâ€™s new on the website (read: promoting new arrivals); or</li><li>Learn beauty tips and trends (read: content marketing.)</li></ul>



<p>This is a brilliant example of engaging order confirmation emails because Cult Beauty knows that its customers are not the same. Thatâ€™s why it guides them to places of different engagement levels, with compelling reasons.</p>



<p>Timing plays a critical role in converting buyers into repeat customers. Unlike Cult Beauty that encourages customers to shop again in its first post-purchase email, ASOS invites users back to its site in its delivery <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/announcement-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">announcement email</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="883" height="886" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email.png" alt="ASOS Shipping Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92280" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email.png 883w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-300x300.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-150x150.png 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-768x771.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-380x381.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-600x602.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-760x763.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-50x50.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-488x490.png 488w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-220x221.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-385x386.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ASOS-Shipping-Confirmation-Email-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px" /></figure></div>



<p>The decision is yours, but the key is finding a balance between a subtle and a direct approach, as well as setting your timing right.</p>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Confirm the Buyerâ€™s Decision</strong></h2>



<p>Have you ever made an impulse buy and regretted it right away?</p>



<p>If so, youâ€™re not alone.</p>



<p>Even when weâ€™re satisfied with our new sweater, it feels good when someone pays a compliment. After all, we want to make sure that we made the right choices.</p>



<p>Order confirmation emails are the perfect way to reaffirm that your customers made the best decision by buying those products from your store not your competitorsâ€™.</p>



<p>Take a look at this example by <a href="https://www.saxo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Saxo</a>, the online bookstore:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="980" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email.png" alt="Saxo Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92340" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-214x300.png 214w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x532.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x840.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-36x50.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-350x490.png 350w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x308.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Saxo-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x539.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>Before going into the order details, Saxo confirms your decision to buy a book from their store, and, more interestingly, they back it by research.</p>



<p>Check this brilliant introduction: â€œStudies suggest that reading improves your memory and makes you more empathic and less stressed. Thereâ€™s a good chance that youâ€™re on your way to becoming a better person! Because we received your order, and weâ€™re looking forward to sending your books.â€</p>



<p>After reaffirming your buying decision, Saxo explains how you can download your ebooks and audiobooks. And before moving onto product details, the company invites you to contact them if you have any questions, with an additional note: â€œWe read audiobooks aloud while you wait on the line.â€</p>



<p>While Saxo chooses a research-backed, bookwormish tone of voice in confirming your decision, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/beardbrand-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Beardbrand</a> takes a different approach:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="650" height="937" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email.png" alt="Beardbrand Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92284" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 650w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-208x300.png 208w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x548.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x865.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-24x35.png 24w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-340x490.png 340w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x317.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x555.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></figure></div>



<p>If your brand voice is closer to Beardbrandâ€™s, donâ€™t be afraid to go bold.</p>



<p>Take a moment to go back to your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">value proposition</a> and think about which problem your products are solving. Maybe you help your customers with their skin issues, or maybe they treat themselves with your monthly boxes.</p>



<p>Find the rational or emotional benefits of your products and give your customers a pat on the back for making a good buying decision.</p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Recommend Complementary Products</strong></h2>



<p>Cross-selling with order confirmation emails is nothing new.</p>



<p>You likely know it well, thanks to <a href="https://www.amazon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Amazon</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="985" height="354" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email.png" alt="Amazon Cross-Sell Email" class="wp-image-92268" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email.png 985w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-300x108.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-768x276.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-380x137.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-600x216.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-760x273.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-97x35.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-139x50.png 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-740x266.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-220x79.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Amazon-Cross-Sell-Email-385x138.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 985px) 100vw, 985px" /></figure></div>



<p>While this approach might work for e-commerce giants like Amazon, you can offer your customers a stronger reason than â€œfrequently bought together.â€</p>



<p>The key to effective cross-selling is recommending genuinely complementary products. In some niches, like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/apparel-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">apparel</a>, itâ€™s easier to make relevant <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product recommendations</a>.</p>



<p>Check out how <a href="http://zalando.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Zalando</a> cross-sells in its order confirmation emails:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="635" height="755" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1.png" alt="Zalando Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92344" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1.png 635w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-252x300.png 252w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-380x452.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-600x713.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-29x35.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-42x50.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-412x490.png 412w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-220x262.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Order-Confirmation-Email-1-385x458.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px" /></figure></div>



<p>Zalando nudges you to return to its website with a powerful <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">call-to-action</a> (CTA) next to each product in your order: <em>Complete Your Look.</em></p>



<p>As opposed to â€œFrequently Bought Together,â€ Zalandoâ€™s CTA speaks directly to you. Plus, it gives you a clear motive to buy more: completing your look with matching clothes and accessories.</p>



<p>When you click the link, Zalando takes you to a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-landing-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">landing page</a> with similar products you might like:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="786" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-1024x786.png" alt="Zalando Recommended Products" class="wp-image-92348" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-1024x786.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-300x230.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-768x590.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-380x292.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-600x461.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-760x583.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-65x50.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-638x490.png 638w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-220x169.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1-385x296.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Recommended-Products-1.png 1214w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If youâ€™re looking for a subtle way to increase your revenue with order confirmation emails, make sure to recommend items that <em>actually </em>complement the customerâ€™s order.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Remember to give your customers a valid reason to shop again. Otherwise, youâ€™ll risk sounding too promotional, trying to sell to people who just bought from you.</p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Promote Your Loyalty Program</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/thank-you-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Thank you pages</a> and order confirmation emails are the two pillars of your post-purchase promotion activities.</p>



<p>If youâ€™re running a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">loyalty program</a>, the best time to promote it to your customers is, undoubtedly, right after they place an order.</p>



<p>Although you shouldnâ€™t take the focus away from the transaction in your order confirmation emails, thereâ€™s a smart way to promote your loyalty program without being intrusive.</p>



<p><a href="https://billigvoks.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Billigvoks</a>, the Danish beauty e-tailer, found a solution to this problem. Check out one of their order confirmation emails:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="876" height="833" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email.png" alt="Billigvoks Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92308" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 876w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-300x285.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-768x730.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x361.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x571.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-760x723.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-515x490.png 515w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x209.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x366.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 876px) 100vw, 876px" /></figure></div>



<p>Billigvoks runs a simple loyalty program: you buy products and earn points that you can use in your future orders.</p>



<p>This way, the company finds a smart way to turn one-time purchases into repeat customers. Since Billigvoksâ€™ loyalty program helps increase the companyâ€™s revenue, they donâ€™t refrain from promoting it in the middle of their order confirmation emails.</p>



<p>By mentioning the points you earned with this order in a non-distracting way, the company both confirms your decision and already makes you think about your next order.</p>



<p>Billigvoks even goes beyond that.</p>



<p>About a month after your purchase, the company sends you a loyalty bonus reminder email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="680" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-1024x680.png" alt="Billigvoks Loyalty Bonus Email" class="wp-image-92304" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-1024x680.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-300x200.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-768x510.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-380x252.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-600x398.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-760x504.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-53x35.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-75x50.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-738x490.png 738w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-220x146.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email-385x256.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billigvoks-Loyalty-Bonus-Email.png 1258w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Instead of simply telling how many points you have, Billigvoks shows you the discounted price of an example product that you could use your loyalty points on. The best part is, they choose this product based on your previous orders.</p>



<p>Post-purchase emails are perfect for promoting your customer loyalty program. Remember to occasionally remind customers of their unused benefits that theyâ€™re <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/fomo-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">missing out on</a>.</p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Encourage Referrals</strong></h2>



<p>Although theyâ€™re automated transactional notifications, order confirmation emails donâ€™t have to be dull and robotic.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.firebox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Firebox</a> is a great example of that. The company successfully incorporates its <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/humor-in-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">humorous</a> brand voice into transactional emails, too.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="1007" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email.png" alt="Firebox Order Confirmation Email" class="wp-image-92324" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-209x300.png 209w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-380x547.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-600x863.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-24x35.png 24w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-341x490.png 341w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-220x316.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-385x554.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>While Fireboxâ€™s tone is rather a safe, feel-good type of humor, be careful about the dose of your humor. After all, you donâ€™t want to confuse people who just gave you their money.</p>



<p>Firebox doesnâ€™t use big words or a fancy design in its order confirmation emails. After simply informing you that <em>next up </em>is <em>dispatch, </em>they appreciate you for being a customer.</p>



<p>After product and delivery details, Firebox has a section dedicated to encouraging <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/referral-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">referrals</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="517" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2.png" alt="Firebox Order Confirmation Email " class="wp-image-92320" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-300x222.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-380x281.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-600x443.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-663x490.png 663w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-220x162.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firebox-Order-Confirmation-Email-2-385x284.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>While asking you to tell your friends about them, the company clearly writes the incentive for both parties.</p>



<p>Just when you bought a bunch of new items and heard all the nice words from Firebox, why wouldnâ€™t you tell your friends about them?</p>



<p>Once again, the timing of your request is crucial, especially if youâ€™re asking for a big favor.</p>



<p>While Firebox asks for referrals at the bottom of confirmation emails, Beardbrand saves a whole email to follow up on its orders.</p>



<p>A few days after making a purchase, Beardbrand sent me an email with the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">subject line</a>, â€œYour friends will thank you,â€ and I opened immediately to learn why:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="995" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1.png" alt="Beardbrand Referral Email" class="wp-image-92288" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1.png 700w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-211x300.png 211w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-380x540.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-600x853.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-345x490.png 345w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-220x313.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Email-1-385x547.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></figure></div>



<p>In this email, Beardbrand confirms your decision one more time (See: Strategy #4) and asks you to refer some friends.</p>



<p>Why? Because your friends will get a special deal, and youâ€™ll be a â€œgrooming guruâ€ in their eyes.</p>



<p>After I clicked the email and filled out a form on Beardbrandâ€™s website, Rikke got this email shortly upon my referral:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="675" height="958" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1.png" alt="Beardbrand Referral Program" class="wp-image-92292" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1.png 675w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-211x300.png 211w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-380x539.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-600x852.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-345x490.png 345w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-220x312.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Beardbrand-Referral-Program-1-385x546.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px" /></figure></div>



<p>After complimenting Rikke for being a lucky man (!), Beardbrand offers her a $25 credit. But thereâ€™s a caveat: it only applies to a specific starter kit.</p>



<p>And if you buy that starter kit, Beardbrand adds another $25 credit to your account. See how they hook you?</p>



<p>Rather than give you a coupon code that applies to any product, Beardbrand directs you to a starting point and makes sure you return for more.</p>



<p>No matter how you manage your referral program, order confirmation emails are a great place to request and follow up on referrals.</p>


